#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MatTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ColorTex;
in mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
float u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
float u_xlat20;
float u_xlat26;
mediump float u_xlat16_31;
mediump float u_xlat16_32;
mediump float u_xlat16_33;
mediump float u_xlat16_34;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
float u_xlat36;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_31 = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_31 = min(max(u_xlat16_31, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_31 = clamp(u_xlat16_31, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_32 = u_xlat16_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xxx;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_2.y * u_xlat16_2.y;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat16_2.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat20 = u_xlat0.x * 0.125 + u_xlat10;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat10);
    u_xlat0.y = u_xlat0.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat20 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_3.xy = max(u_xlat0.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(_SHScale);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0.xxxx + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_0 = -abs(u_xlat16_0) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0 = min(max(u_xlat16_0, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0 = clamp(u_xlat16_0, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_33 = dot(u_xlat16_0, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_32 = u_xlat16_32 + u_xlat16_33;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_32 = min(max(u_xlat16_32, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_32 = clamp(u_xlat16_32, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_33 = dot(u_xlat16_0, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_32) * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = (-u_xlat16_5.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_32) + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_31) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_33 + u_xlat16_31;
    u_xlat16_31 = max(u_xlat16_31, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_31 = min(u_xlat16_31, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_32 = u_xlat16_31 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_31 * u_xlat16_31;
    u_xlat16_7.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_7.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_7.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat16_7.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = max(u_xlat36, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = abs(u_xlat16_34) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_34 = min(u_xlat16_34, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_33 * u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat16_34 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_34 = (-u_xlat16_34) + 1.0;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35 + u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat16_33 / u_xlat36;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_33 * u_xlat16_33 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_33 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_33;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat36;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat16_32 * u_xlat36;
    u_xlat36 = min(u_xlat36, 100.0);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat36 = min(max(u_xlat36, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat36 = clamp(u_xlat36, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat36) + u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_32 = u_xlat36 * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_31) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_31 * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat16_31 + 1.0;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat36;
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_3.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot((-u_xlat8.xyz), u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x + u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * (-u_xlat16_3.xxx) + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_31);
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_7.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_31 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_31 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_31 = max(u_xlat16_31, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_31 = log2(u_xlat16_31);
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_31 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_31 = exp2(u_xlat16_31);
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_31 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_31);
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_33);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz * u_xlat6.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_5.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat36 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_31 = (-u_xlat36) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_31 + u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_34 / u_xlat16_31;
    u_xlat16_33 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_33);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_33) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_33 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_33 = min(max(u_xlat16_33, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_33 = clamp(u_xlat16_33, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_31 * u_xlat16_33 + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_33 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_33 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_33;
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_31 * u_xlat16_33;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_31 = min(max(u_xlat16_31, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_31 = clamp(u_xlat16_31, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_31 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_31 * u_xlat16_31;
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_31 * u_xlat16_33;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_31);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = max(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = min(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss)) * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = (-u_xlat8.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat6.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat8.zxy) + (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat6.yzx * (-u_xlat8.zxy);
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat8.yzx) * u_xlat6.zxy + (-u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat6.x = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat6.z = dot((-u_xlat8.xyz), u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat6.y = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat26 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat26 = inversesqrt(u_xlat26);
    u_xlat6.xy = vec2(u_xlat26) * u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = texture(_MatTex, u_xlat6.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_32) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * _MatTexColor.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);

    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz / u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = min(u_xlat6.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHC;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(1) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _NormalScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SpecularColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MetallicOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AOScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Emiss;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _EmissColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHshadow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec3 _AddLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightDarkcolor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightLerp;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightShadowScale;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color3;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color4;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat1.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

#endif

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ColorTex;
in mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
bool u_xlatb2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
vec3 u_xlat14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
mediump float u_xlat16_17;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_21;
mediump float u_xlat16_34;
float u_xlat35;
float u_xlat36;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
mediump float u_xlat16_38;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
float u_xlat40;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0.xxxx + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_0 = -abs(u_xlat16_0) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0 = min(max(u_xlat16_0, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0 = clamp(u_xlat16_0, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_0, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_0, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 + u_xlat16_15.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_34 = min(max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat3.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = (-u_xlat16_1.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_6.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_6.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = max(u_xlat36, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xy = u_xlat16_5.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_5.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyw = u_xlat16_5.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyw;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = abs(u_xlat16_34) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_34 = min(u_xlat16_34, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_38 = (-u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat16_34 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_2.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x + u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_17 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_34 = (-u_xlat16_34) + 1.0;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat16_17 * u_xlat16_17 + u_xlat16_38;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat16_6.x / u_xlat35;
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_6.x * u_xlat16_6.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_38 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_38;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat35 * u_xlat35;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat35 * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat35 = min(u_xlat35, 100.0);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat35) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat35 = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat35 = min(max(u_xlat35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat35 = clamp(u_xlat35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat35) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * vec3(u_xlat35) + u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat16_5.y * u_xlat16_5.y;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat16_5.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat35 * 0.125 + u_xlat36;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat35 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat36);
    u_xlat8.y = u_xlat35 + 0.125;
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat40 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_10.xy = max(u_xlat8.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xy = u_xlat16_10.xy * vec2(_SHScale);
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_10.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_39 = min(max(u_xlat16_39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_39 = clamp(u_xlat16_39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.x = dot((-u_xlat7.xyz), u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x + u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * (-u_xlat16_6.xxx) + (-u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = (-u_xlat16_4.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat35 * u_xlat35;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_39 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_0 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_0.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_38) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * u_xlat3.xyz + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat35 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_37 = (-u_xlat35) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_37 + u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 / u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat16_37 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_37 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_37);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_37 = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat16_5.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_37 = min(max(u_xlat16_37, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_37 = clamp(u_xlat16_37, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_37 + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_37 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_37 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_37;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_34 = min(max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_34 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;

    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;

    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz / u_xlat14.xyz;

    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb2) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_3.x;

	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LODFade;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightData;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightIndices[2];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_ProbesOcclusion;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SpecCube0_HDR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_DynamicLightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHC;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(1) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _NormalScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SpecularColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MetallicOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AOScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Emiss;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _EmissColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RampTexColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RampTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHshadow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec3 _AddLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightDarkcolor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightLerp;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightShadowScale;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Rimlightoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color3;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _metalv4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _roughv4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _BlendMode;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat1.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

#endif

precision highp float;

uniform 	vec4 _MainLightPosition;

#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _ColorTex;
in mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
bool u_xlatb3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_16;
mediump float u_xlat16_18;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_21;
float u_xlat26;
mediump float u_xlat16_34;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
float u_xlat36;
float u_xlat37;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
mediump float u_xlat16_40;
float u_xlat41;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0.xxxx + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_0 = -abs(u_xlat16_0) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0 = min(max(u_xlat16_0, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0 = clamp(u_xlat16_0, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_0, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_0, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 + u_xlat16_5.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_34 = min(max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat4.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-u_xlat16_2.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_3.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_35 + u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat16_34 = max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_34 = min(u_xlat16_34, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_34 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat16_7.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_7.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_7.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat16_7.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = max(u_xlat36, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16.xy = u_xlat16_16.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_16.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_16.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = u_xlat16_16.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_16.xyz, u_xlat16_16.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = u_xlat16_16.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_16.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = abs(u_xlat16_39) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_39 = min(u_xlat16_39, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_18 = (-u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat16_39 + 1.0;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_7.x + u_xlat16_18;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat16_5.x / u_xlat36;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_5.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat36;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat36;
    u_xlat36 = min(u_xlat36, 100.0);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat16_16.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat36 = min(max(u_xlat36, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat36 = clamp(u_xlat36, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(u_xlat36) + u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat36 * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat16_16.y * u_xlat16_16.y;
    u_xlat37 = u_xlat16_16.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat41 = u_xlat36 * 0.125 + u_xlat37;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat37);
    u_xlat9.y = u_xlat36 + 0.125;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat41 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_10.xy = max(u_xlat9.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xy = u_xlat16_10.xy * vec2(_SHScale);
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_10.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_40 = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_40 = min(max(u_xlat16_40, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_40 = clamp(u_xlat16_40, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_40);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.x = dot((-u_xlat8.xyz), u_xlat16_16.xyz);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x + u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_16.xyz * (-u_xlat16_6.xxx) + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_34) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat16_34 + 1.0;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat36;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_7.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_0 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_0.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_34 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_34 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_34 = max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_34 = log2(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_34 = exp2(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz * u_xlat4.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat16_16.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_34 = min(max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat16_39) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_16.x = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat4.x = min(u_xlat16_16.x, 0.959999979);
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat4.x * _RampTex_ST.x + _RampTex_ST.z;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat36 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_16.x = (-u_xlat36) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_16.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_16.x + u_xlat26;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x / u_xlat16_16.x;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_34 + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_5.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_5.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3

    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_8.yyy + u_xlat16_1.xyz;

    u_xlat10_8.xyz = texture2D(_MatTex, u_xlat28.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat10_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * _MatTexColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat10_6.yyy + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat17.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat17.xyz = u_xlat17.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat17.xyz = u_xlat17.xyz / u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat17.xyz = min(u_xlat17.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat17.xyz;
    u_xlatb17 = _BlendMode==0.0;
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb17) ? 1.0 : u_xlat10_6.x;
    return;
}

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat1.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;

#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_34 = min(max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xxx;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_2.y * u_xlat16_2.y;
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat16_2.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat0.x * 0.125 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat11);
    u_xlat0.y = u_xlat0.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat22 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_3.xy = max(u_xlat0.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(_SHScale);
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0.xxxx + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_0 = -abs(u_xlat16_0) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0 = min(max(u_xlat16_0, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0 = clamp(u_xlat16_0, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(u_xlat16_0, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 + u_xlat16_36;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);

    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * _color2.xyz;

    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(u_xlat16_0, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);

    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = (-u_xlat16_5.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_35) + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_36 + u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat16_34 = max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_34 = min(u_xlat16_34, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_34 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat16_7.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_7.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_7.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat39 = dot(u_xlat16_7.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
    u_xlat39 = max(u_xlat39, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat39);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat39) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_37 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_37 = abs(u_xlat16_37) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_37 = min(u_xlat16_37, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_36 * u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_37) * u_xlat16_37 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_37 = (-u_xlat16_37) + 1.0;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat16_38 * u_xlat16_38 + u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat16_36 / u_xlat39;
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_36 * u_xlat16_36 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_36 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_36;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat39 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat39 = min(u_xlat39, 100.0);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat39) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat39 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat39 = min(max(u_xlat39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat39 = clamp(u_xlat39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat39) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat39) + u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat39 * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_34) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat16_34 + 1.0;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat39 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_3.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot((-u_xlat8.xyz), u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x + u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * (-u_xlat16_3.xxx) + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_7.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_34 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_34 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_34 = max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_34 = log2(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_34 = exp2(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz * u_xlat6.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_5.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat39 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_34 = (-u_xlat39) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_37 * u_xlat16_34 + u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_37 / u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_36 = min(max(u_xlat16_36, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_36 = clamp(u_xlat16_36, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_36 + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_36 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_36 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_36;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_36;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_34 = min(max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_34 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_36;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = max(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = min(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_6.zzz * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat8.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat9.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat8.zxy) + (-u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat28.x = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat28.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat28.x);
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat28.xxx * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = (-u_xlat8.zxy) * u_xlat9.yzx;
    u_xlat10.xyz = (-u_xlat8.yzx) * u_xlat9.zxy + (-u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat9.x = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat9.z = dot((-u_xlat8.xyz), u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat28.x = dot(u_xlat10.xyz, u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat28.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat28.x);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat28.xxx * u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat9.y = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat28.x = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat28.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat28.x);
    u_xlat28.xy = u_xlat28.xx * u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat28.xy = u_xlat28.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = texture(_MatTex, u_xlat28.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * _MatTexColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_6.yyy + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat17.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat17.xyz = u_xlat17.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat17.xyz = u_xlat17.xyz / u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat17.xyz = min(u_xlat17.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat17.xyz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb17 = !!(_BlendMode==0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb17 = _BlendMode==0.0;
#endif
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb17) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_6.x;
    return;
}

    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_4.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_14.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_14.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_14.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_4.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_8.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss)) * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat10_2.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz / u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = min(u_xlat1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat1.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;

mediump vec3 u_xlat16_16;

mediump float u_xlat16_25;

void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat1.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat2.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat1.zxy) + (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat31 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat31 = inversesqrt(u_xlat31);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat31) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat1.zxy) * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat1.yzx) * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat31 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat31 = inversesqrt(u_xlat31);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat31) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xxx;
    u_xlat3.y = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat3.x = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot((-u_xlat1.xyz), u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = abs(u_xlat16_5.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(u_xlat16_5.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat16_5.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xx * u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_21 = texture(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_0 = vec4(u_xlat16_21) + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_0 = -abs(u_xlat16_0) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0 = min(max(u_xlat16_0, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0 = clamp(u_xlat16_0, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(u_xlat16_0, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_25 = u_xlat16_2.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x + u_xlat16_25;
    u_xlat16_15.x = max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(u_xlat16_15.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_25 = (-u_xlat16_15.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_25 = u_xlat16_25 * u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat16_15.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat21 * u_xlat21;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_25 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_1.xyw = textureLod(_MatcapTex, u_xlat1.xy, u_xlat16_15.x).xyz;
    u_xlat32 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat32 = min(max(u_xlat32, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat32 = clamp(u_xlat32, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat32 * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyw * u_xlat16_15.xxx;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * _MatcapColor.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_4.y * u_xlat16_4.y;
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat16_4.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat31 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat11);
    u_xlat1.y = u_xlat1.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat31 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_6.xy = max(u_xlat1.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_6.xy = u_xlat16_6.xy * vec2(_SHScale);
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = u_xlat16_6.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_16.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(u_xlat16_0, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 + u_xlat16_36;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_34 = min(max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat1.xyw = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat1.xyw + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat16_8.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat32) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_34 = min(max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * u_xlat1.xyw + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat21 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_34 = (-u_xlat21) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_34 + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_5.x / u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_4.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_14.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_14.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_14.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_4.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_8.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss)) * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz / u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = min(u_xlat1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;

    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;

    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz / u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = min(u_xlat1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat1.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MatcapTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ColorTex;
in mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
float u_xlat12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
mediump float u_xlat16_16;
float u_xlat23;
mediump float u_xlat16_23;
mediump float u_xlat16_26;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_27;
float u_xlat34;
float u_xlat35;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat1.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat2.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat1.zxy) + (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat34 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat34);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat1.zxy) * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat1.yzx) * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat34 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat34);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xxx;
    u_xlat3.y = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat3.x = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot((-u_xlat1.xyz), u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = abs(u_xlat16_5.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xx * u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_23 = texture(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_0 = vec4(u_xlat16_23) + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_0 = -abs(u_xlat16_0) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0 = min(max(u_xlat16_0, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0 = clamp(u_xlat16_0, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_16 = dot(u_xlat16_0, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_27.x = u_xlat16_2.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_16 + u_xlat16_27.x;
    u_xlat16_5.y = max(u_xlat16_16, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_5.xy = min(u_xlat16_5.xy, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_27.x = (-u_xlat16_5.y) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_27.x = u_xlat16_27.x * u_xlat16_5.y;
    u_xlat23 = u_xlat16_5.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat23 = u_xlat23 * u_xlat23;
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_27.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_1.xyw = textureLod(_MatcapTex, u_xlat1.xy, u_xlat16_16).xyz;
    u_xlat35 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat35 = min(max(u_xlat35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat35 = clamp(u_xlat35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat35 * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyw * vec3(u_xlat16_16);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * _MatcapColor.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_4.y * u_xlat16_4.y;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat16_4.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + u_xlat12;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat12);
    u_xlat1.y = u_xlat1.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat34 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_27.xy = max(u_xlat1.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_27.xy = u_xlat16_27.xy * vec2(_SHScale);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_27.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_27.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_27.x = dot(u_xlat16_0, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_37 + u_xlat16_27.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_37 = min(max(u_xlat16_37, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_37 = clamp(u_xlat16_37, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat1.xyw = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * u_xlat1.xyw + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat16_9.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_37) + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat35) * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_37 = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_37 = min(max(u_xlat16_37, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_37 = clamp(u_xlat16_37, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat1.xyw + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_37 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_37 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_37);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_7.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-u_xlat16_5.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_26 = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat16_26, 0.959999979);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * _RampTex_ST.x + _RampTex_ST.z;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat23 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_26 = (-u_xlat23) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_26 = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_26 + u_xlat34;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x / u_xlat16_26;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_4.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_15.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_4.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xzw = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_9.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_5.xzw + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xzw = vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss)) * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xzw * u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat1.y = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_RampTex, u_xlat1.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_16) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * _RampTexColor.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);

    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz / u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = min(u_xlat1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}
