#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

#endif

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MatcapTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _ColorTex;
in mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
vec3 u_xlat11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
float u_xlat15;
uint u_xlatu15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_18;
float u_xlat30;
int u_xlati30;
bool u_xlatb30;
float u_xlat31;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_33;
float u_xlat45;
mediump float u_xlat16_45;
bool u_xlatb45;
float u_xlat46;
bool u_xlatb46;
mediump float u_xlat16_47;
mediump float u_xlat16_48;
mediump float u_xlat16_49;
mediump float u_xlat16_50;
float u_xlat52;
float u_xlat54;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_1.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb46 = !!(_BlendMode==0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb46 = _BlendMode==0.0;
#endif
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb46) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb45 = !!(u_xlat16_0.y>=u_xlat16_0.z);
#else
    u_xlatb45 = u_xlat16_0.y>=u_xlat16_0.z;
#endif
    u_xlat16_18.x = (u_xlatb45) ? 1.0 : 0.0;
    u_xlat16_33.xy = (-u_xlat16_0.zy) + u_xlat16_0.yz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = float(1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.y = float(-1.0);
    u_xlat16_5.xy = u_xlat16_18.xx * u_xlat16_33.xy + u_xlat16_0.zy;
    u_xlat16_5.zw = u_xlat16_18.xx * u_xlat16_4.xy + vec2(-1.0, 0.666666687);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb45 = !!(u_xlat16_0.x>=u_xlat16_5.x);
#else
    u_xlatb45 = u_xlat16_0.x>=u_xlat16_5.x;
#endif
    u_xlat16_18.x = (u_xlatb45) ? 1.0 : 0.0;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = (-u_xlat16_5.xyw);
    u_xlat16_4.w = (-u_xlat16_0.x);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_0.x + u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_6.yzw = u_xlat16_4.yzw + u_xlat16_5.yzx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xxx * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyw;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_6.w + u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_33.x = min(u_xlat16_4.y, u_xlat16_18.x);
    u_xlat16_33.x = (-u_xlat16_33.x) + u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_18.x = (-u_xlat16_4.y) + u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_33.x * 6.0 + 1.00000001e-07;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x / u_xlat16_48;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x + u_xlat16_4.z;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_4.x + 1.00000001e-07;
    u_xlat16_33.x = u_xlat16_33.x / u_xlat16_48;
    u_xlat16_18.x = abs(u_xlat16_18.x) + _ColorHUE;
    u_xlat16_33.x = u_xlat16_33.x + _ColorSaturation;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xxx * vec3(6.0, 6.0, 6.0) + vec3(-3.0, -2.0, -4.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = abs(u_xlat7.xyz) * vec3(1.0, -1.0, -1.0) + vec3(-1.0, 2.0, 2.0);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat7.xyz = min(max(u_xlat7.xyz, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat7.xyz = clamp(u_xlat7.xyz, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * u_xlat16_33.xxx + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_45 = texture(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_4 = vec4(u_xlat16_45) + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_4 = u_xlat16_4 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_4 = -abs(u_xlat16_4) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4 = min(max(u_xlat16_4, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4 = clamp(u_xlat16_4, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_4.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_50 = dot(u_xlat16_4, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 + u_xlat16_50;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_47 = min(max(u_xlat16_47, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_47 = clamp(u_xlat16_47, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_4, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x + u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss));
    u_xlat16_3.x = max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(u_xlat16_3.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-u_xlat16_5.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_47) + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_8.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_8.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat45 = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_8.xyz);
    u_xlat45 = max(u_xlat45, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat45 = inversesqrt(u_xlat45);
    u_xlat1.xzw = vec3(u_xlat45) * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_2.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_49 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_49 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat9.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * u_xlat16_18.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_47) * u_xlat7.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat45 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat45 = min(max(u_xlat45, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat45 = clamp(u_xlat45, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_18.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat1.xzw);
    u_xlat16_18.x = abs(u_xlat16_18.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_18.x = min(u_xlat16_18.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat52 = u_xlat16_2.y * u_xlat16_2.y;
    u_xlat54 = u_xlat16_2.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat52 * 0.125 + u_xlat54;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat10.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat52 = u_xlat52 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat54);
    u_xlat10.y = u_xlat52 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_33.xy = max(u_xlat10.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_33.xy = u_xlat16_33.xy * vec2(_SHScale);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_33.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_33.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_33.x = u_xlat45 * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat10.xyz = (-u_xlat1.zwx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat10.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat1.wxz) + (-u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat52 = dot(u_xlat10.xyz, u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat52 = inversesqrt(u_xlat52);
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat52) * u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xyz = (-u_xlat1.wxz) * u_xlat10.yzx;
    u_xlat11.xyz = (-u_xlat1.zwx) * u_xlat10.zxy + (-u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat52 = dot(u_xlat11.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat52 = inversesqrt(u_xlat52);
    u_xlat11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat52) * u_xlat11.xyz;
    u_xlat10.x = dot(u_xlat10.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat10.y = dot(u_xlat11.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat10.z = dot((-u_xlat1.xzw), u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat10.xyz, u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xz = u_xlat1.xx * u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat1.xz = u_xlat1.xz * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_48 = (-u_xlat16_3.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_48 * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_48 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = textureLod(_MatcapTex, u_xlat1.xz, u_xlat16_48).xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_33.xxx * u_xlat16_1.xzw;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * _MatcapColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = vec3(u_xlat45) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_48 = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_48 = min(max(u_xlat16_48, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_48 = clamp(u_xlat16_48, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_48) * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat7.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_48 = (-u_xlat16_18.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat31 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_49 = (-u_xlat1.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_48 * u_xlat16_49 + u_xlat31;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_48 / u_xlat16_49;
    u_xlat16_49 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_49 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_49) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_49 = dot(u_xlat16_12.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_49 = min(max(u_xlat16_49, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_49 = clamp(u_xlat16_49, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_50 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_48 * u_xlat16_49 + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_49 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_50;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_48 * u_xlat16_49;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_48 = min(max(u_xlat16_48, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_48 = clamp(u_xlat16_48, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_48 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_48 * u_xlat16_48;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_48 * u_xlat16_49;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_5.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_48) * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = max(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = min(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat0.x = min(u_xlat16_48, 0.959999979);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * _RampTex_ST.x + _RampTex_ST.z;
    u_xlat0.y = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_RampTex, u_xlat0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_33.xxx * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * _RampTexColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_1.yyy + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_33.x = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlatu0 = uint(int(u_xlat16_33.x));
    u_xlat16_33.x = (-u_xlat16_18.x) * u_xlat16_18.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_47 * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_18.x + u_xlat16_33.x;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat16_47 / u_xlat15;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat15;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_3.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat16_47;
    u_xlat15 = min(u_xlat15, 100.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat45) + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = max(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = min(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    for(uint u_xlatu_loop_1 = uint(0u) ; u_xlatu_loop_1<u_xlatu0 ; u_xlatu_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat30 = float(int(u_xlatu_loop_1));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb45 = !!(u_xlat30<2.0);
#else
        u_xlatb45 = u_xlat30<2.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_6.xy = (bool(u_xlatb45)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat1.x = u_xlat30 + -2.0;
        u_xlat30 = (u_xlatb45) ? u_xlat30 : u_xlat1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb30 = !!(u_xlat30<1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb30 = u_xlat30<1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_47 = (u_xlatb30) ? u_xlat16_6.x : u_xlat16_6.y;
        u_xlati30 = int(u_xlat16_47);
        u_xlat1.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPosition[u_xlati30].xyz;
        u_xlat45 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat45 = max(u_xlat45, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat46 = inversesqrt(u_xlat45);
        u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat46) * u_xlat1.xyz;
        u_xlat46 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat45);
        u_xlat45 = u_xlat45 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati30].x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati30].y;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat45 = min(max(u_xlat45, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat45 = clamp(u_xlat45, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat45 = u_xlat45 * u_xlat46;
        u_xlat16_47 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDir[u_xlati30].xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati30].z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati30].w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_47 = min(max(u_xlat16_47, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_47 = clamp(u_xlat16_47, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 * u_xlat16_47;
        u_xlat45 = u_xlat45 * u_xlat16_47;
        u_xlat16_47 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_47 = min(max(u_xlat16_47, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_47 = clamp(u_xlat16_47, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_47) * _AdditionalLightsColor[u_xlati30].xyz;
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat45) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
        u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);

    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));

void main()
{

    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

#endif

precision highp float;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color3;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _metalv4;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _BlendMode;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;

#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _ColorTex;
in mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
vec3 u_xlat11;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
uint u_xlatu15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_18;
float u_xlat30;
int u_xlati30;
bool u_xlatb30;
float u_xlat31;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_33;
float u_xlat45;
mediump float u_xlat16_45;
bool u_xlatb45;
float u_xlat46;
bool u_xlatb46;
mediump float u_xlat16_47;
mediump float u_xlat16_48;
mediump float u_xlat16_49;
mediump float u_xlat16_50;
float u_xlat53;
float u_xlat54;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_1.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb46 = !!(_BlendMode==0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb46 = _BlendMode==0.0;
#endif
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb46) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_45 = texture(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_4 = vec4(u_xlat16_45) + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_4 = u_xlat16_4 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_4 = -abs(u_xlat16_4) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4 = min(max(u_xlat16_4, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4 = clamp(u_xlat16_4, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_4.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_50 = dot(u_xlat16_4, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 + u_xlat16_50;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_47 = min(max(u_xlat16_47, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_47 = clamp(u_xlat16_47, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_4, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x + u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss));
    u_xlat16_3.x = max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(u_xlat16_3.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-u_xlat16_5.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_47) + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_7.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_7.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat45 = dot(u_xlat16_7.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
    u_xlat45 = max(u_xlat45, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat45 = inversesqrt(u_xlat45);
    u_xlat1.xzw = vec3(u_xlat45) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_2.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_49 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_49 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat8.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_18.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_47) * u_xlat9.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat45 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat45 = min(max(u_xlat45, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat45 = clamp(u_xlat45, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_18.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat1.xzw);
    u_xlat16_18.x = abs(u_xlat16_18.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_18.x = min(u_xlat16_18.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat53 = u_xlat16_2.y * u_xlat16_2.y;
    u_xlat54 = u_xlat16_2.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat53 * 0.125 + u_xlat54;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat10.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat53 = u_xlat53 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat54);
    u_xlat10.y = u_xlat53 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_33.xy = max(u_xlat10.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_33.xy = u_xlat16_33.xy * vec2(_SHScale);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_33.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_33.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_33.x = u_xlat45 * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_49 = (-u_xlat16_18.x) * u_xlat16_18.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_47 * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat53 = u_xlat16_50 * u_xlat16_50 + u_xlat16_49;
    u_xlat53 = u_xlat16_47 / u_xlat53;
    u_xlat53 = u_xlat53 * u_xlat53;
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_3.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat53 = u_xlat53 * u_xlat16_49;
    u_xlat53 = min(u_xlat53, 100.0);
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat53) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat45) * u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_49 = dot((-u_xlat1.xzw), u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_49 + u_xlat16_49;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_49)) + (-u_xlat1.xzw);
    u_xlat16_49 = (-u_xlat16_3.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_49;
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_49 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_12 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_12.xyz, u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_12.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_49 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_49 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_49 = max(u_xlat16_49, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_49 = log2(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_49 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_49 = exp2(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_49 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 * u_xlat16_47 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_47 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_47;
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat16_13.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_47);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(u_xlat45) + u_xlat11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_47 = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_47 = min(max(u_xlat16_47, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_47 = clamp(u_xlat16_47, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_47) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat1.xzw * u_xlat9.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_47 = (-u_xlat16_18.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat31 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat1.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_47 * u_xlat16_3.x + u_xlat31;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 / u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_18.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 * u_xlat16_3.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_3.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 * u_xlat16_3.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_47 = min(max(u_xlat16_47, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_47 = clamp(u_xlat16_47, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_47 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 * u_xlat16_47;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_5.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_47) * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = max(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = min(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = min(u_xlat16_48, 0.959999979);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * _RampTex_ST.x + _RampTex_ST.z;
    u_xlat0.y = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_RampTex, u_xlat0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_33.xxx * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * _RampTexColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_1.yyy + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_47 = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlatu0 = uint(int(u_xlat16_47));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz * vec3(u_xlat45) + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    for(uint u_xlatu_loop_1 = uint(0u) ; u_xlatu_loop_1<u_xlatu0 ; u_xlatu_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat30 = float(int(u_xlatu_loop_1));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb45 = !!(u_xlat30<2.0);
#else
        u_xlatb45 = u_xlat30<2.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_6.xy = (bool(u_xlatb45)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat1.x = u_xlat30 + -2.0;
        u_xlat30 = (u_xlatb45) ? u_xlat30 : u_xlat1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb30 = !!(u_xlat30<1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb30 = u_xlat30<1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_47 = (u_xlatb30) ? u_xlat16_6.x : u_xlat16_6.y;
        u_xlati30 = int(u_xlat16_47);
        u_xlat1.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPosition[u_xlati30].xyz;
        u_xlat45 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat45 = max(u_xlat45, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat46 = inversesqrt(u_xlat45);
        u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat46) * u_xlat1.xyz;
        u_xlat46 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat45);
        u_xlat45 = u_xlat45 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati30].x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati30].y;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat45 = min(max(u_xlat45, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat45 = clamp(u_xlat45, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat45 = u_xlat45 * u_xlat46;
        u_xlat16_47 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDir[u_xlati30].xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati30].z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati30].w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_47 = min(max(u_xlat16_47, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_47 = clamp(u_xlat16_47, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 * u_xlat16_47;
        u_xlat45 = u_xlat45 * u_xlat16_47;
        u_xlat16_47 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_47 = min(max(u_xlat16_47, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_47 = clamp(u_xlat16_47, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_47) * _AdditionalLightsColor[u_xlati30].xyz;
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat45) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
        u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);

    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    return;
}

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;

{

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHC;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(1) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _NormalScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SpecularColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MetallicOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AOScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Emiss;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _EmissColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHshadow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec3 _AddLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightDarkcolor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightLerp;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec3 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Rimlightoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat1.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

#endif

precision highp float;

uniform 	vec4 _MainLightPosition;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightColor;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightShadowParams;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS

#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
in mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump float u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
vec2 u_xlat9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
vec3 u_xlat11;
bool u_xlatb11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump float u_xlat16_14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_21;
mediump float u_xlat16_26;
float u_xlat33;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
float u_xlat39;
void main()
{
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(vs_TEXCOORD7.xy,vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
    u_xlat16_0 = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_1.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_0 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb11 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb11 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb11 || u_xlatb0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_2.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_2.w + _MetallicOffset;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_36 = min(max(u_xlat16_36, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_36 = clamp(u_xlat16_36, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = abs(u_xlat16_4.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-u_xlat16_4.x) * u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_26 = u_xlat16_2.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_26 = max(u_xlat16_26, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_26 = min(u_xlat16_26, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_26 * u_xlat16_26;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_37 * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_5.x + u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat16_37 / u_xlat33;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_37 * u_xlat16_37 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat33;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_26 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat33 = min(u_xlat33, 100.0);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-u_xlat16_2.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_36) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat33 = min(max(u_xlat33, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat33 = clamp(u_xlat33, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(u_xlat33) + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_1.x + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_36 = min(max(u_xlat16_36, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_36 = clamp(u_xlat16_36, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_3.y;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat16_3.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat7.x = u_xlat33 * 0.125 + u_xlat39;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat39);
    u_xlat9.y = u_xlat33 + 0.125;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat7.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_10.xy = max(u_xlat9.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xy = u_xlat16_10.xy * vec2(_SHScale);
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_10.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot((-u_xlat0.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_36 + u_xlat16_36;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_36)) + (-u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = (-u_xlat16_26) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_36 * u_xlat16_26;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_26 + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_36 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_5 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_5.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_36 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_36 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_36 = max(u_xlat16_36, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_36 = log2(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_36 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_36 = exp2(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_36 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz * u_xlat6.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(u_xlat16_15.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_14 = (-u_xlat0.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_14 + u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_4.x / u_xlat16_14;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat16_3.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_14 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_14 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_14;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat16_3.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_3.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_14;
    u_xlat16_14 = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_14 + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_2.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = max(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = min(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss)) * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;

    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

{

UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerDraw {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LODFade;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightData;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightIndices[2];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_ProbesOcclusion;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SpecCube0_HDR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_DynamicLightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHC;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(1) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _NormalScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SpecularColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MetallicOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AOScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Emiss;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _EmissColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHshadow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec3 _AddLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightDarkcolor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightLerp;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec3 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Rimlightoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color3;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _metalv4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _roughv4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat1.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

#endif

precision highp float;

uniform 	vec4 _MainLightPosition;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightColor;

#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _ColorTex;
in mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
bool u_xlatb11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_16;
mediump float u_xlat16_18;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_21;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
float u_xlat36;
float u_xlat37;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
mediump float u_xlat16_40;
float u_xlat41;
void main()
{
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(vs_TEXCOORD7.xy,vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
    u_xlat16_0.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_1.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_0.x * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb11 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb11 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb11 || u_xlatb0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0.xxxx + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_0 = -abs(u_xlat16_0) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0 = min(max(u_xlat16_0, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0 = clamp(u_xlat16_0, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_0, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_0, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_16.x = u_xlat16_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 + u_xlat16_16.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat4.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = (-u_xlat16_2.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_35) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_7.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_7.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat37 = dot(u_xlat16_7.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
    u_xlat37 = max(u_xlat37, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat37 = inversesqrt(u_xlat37);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat37) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xy = u_xlat16_6.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyw = u_xlat16_6.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyw;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = abs(u_xlat16_35) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_35 = min(u_xlat16_35, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_39 = (-u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_35 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_3.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x + u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat16_5.x = max(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(u_xlat16_5.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat16_35 = (-u_xlat16_35) + 1.0;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat16_18 * u_xlat16_18 + u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat16_7.x / u_xlat36;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_7.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_39 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat36;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_5.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat36 = min(u_xlat36, 100.0);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat36 = min(max(u_xlat36, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat36 = clamp(u_xlat36, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_16.xyz * vec3(u_xlat36) + u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_40 = u_xlat16_1.x + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_40 = min(max(u_xlat16_40, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_40 = clamp(u_xlat16_40, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat16_6.y * u_xlat16_6.y;
    u_xlat37 = u_xlat16_6.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat41 = u_xlat36 * 0.125 + u_xlat37;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat37);
    u_xlat9.y = u_xlat36 + 0.125;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat41 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_10.xy = max(u_xlat9.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xy = u_xlat16_10.xy * vec2(_SHScale);
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_10.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = u_xlat16_16.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_40) * u_xlat16_16.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_16.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16.x = dot((-u_xlat8.xyz), u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_16.x = u_xlat16_16.x + u_xlat16_16.x;
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * (-u_xlat16_16.xxx) + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_5.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat16_5.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat36;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_7.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_0 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_16.xyz, u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_0.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_5.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = max(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_5.x = log2(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_5.x = exp2(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xxx;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz * u_xlat4.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat36 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat36) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_5.x + u_xlat4.x;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 / u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(max(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_5.x = clamp(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_5.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_5.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_5.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_35 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_5.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_2.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = min(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss)) * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat4.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz / u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = min(u_xlat3.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

{

    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_38 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * u_xlat16_38;
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_17.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_38;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_2.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = min(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss)) * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat10_3.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat4.y = 0.0;
    u_xlat10_3.xyz = texture2D(_RampTex, u_xlat4.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_5) * u_xlat10_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * _RampTexColor.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat4.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz / u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = min(u_xlat3.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat1.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;

UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ColorTex;
in mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
bool u_xlatb2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
mediump float u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump float u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_17;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_19;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_22;
float u_xlat28;
mediump float u_xlat16_29;
mediump float u_xlat16_31;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
bool u_xlatb36;
float u_xlat38;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
float u_xlat40;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
float u_xlat44;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(vs_TEXCOORD7.xy,vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
    u_xlat16_36 = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_1.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_36 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb36 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb36 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb2 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb2 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb36 = u_xlatb36 || u_xlatb2;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb36) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0.xxxx + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_0 = -abs(u_xlat16_0) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0 = min(max(u_xlat16_0, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0 = clamp(u_xlat16_0, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_0, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_5 = dot(u_xlat16_0, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 + u_xlat16_17.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_39 = min(max(u_xlat16_39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_39 = clamp(u_xlat16_39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat4.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = (-u_xlat16_3.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_39) + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_2.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_5 + u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_39 = max(u_xlat16_39, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_39 = min(u_xlat16_39, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_5 = u_xlat16_39 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_7.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_7.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_7.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat38 = dot(u_xlat16_7.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
    u_xlat38 = max(u_xlat38, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat38 = inversesqrt(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat38) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xy = u_xlat16_6.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_7.x);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xxx;
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = abs(u_xlat16_7.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_7.x = min(u_xlat16_7.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_19.x = u_xlat16_42 * u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat16_31 = (-u_xlat16_7.x) * u_xlat16_7.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat16_19.x * u_xlat16_19.x + u_xlat16_31;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat16_42 / u_xlat38;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 * u_xlat16_42 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat38;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat16_5;
    u_xlat38 = min(u_xlat38, 100.0);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat38) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat38 = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat38 = min(max(u_xlat38, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat38 = clamp(u_xlat38, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat38) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_19.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * vec3(u_xlat38) + u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5 = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat38;
    u_xlat16_5 = u_xlat16_5 * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_10 = u_xlat16_1.x + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_10 = min(max(u_xlat16_10, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_10 = clamp(u_xlat16_10, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat16_6.y * u_xlat16_6.y;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat16_6.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat44 = u_xlat38 * 0.125 + u_xlat40;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat40);
    u_xlat9.y = u_xlat38 + 0.125;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat44 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_22.xy = max(u_xlat9.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_22.xy = u_xlat16_22.xy * vec2(_SHScale);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_22.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_10) * u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_19.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xyz + u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.x = dot((-u_xlat8.xyz), u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x + u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * (-u_xlat16_17.xxx) + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_19.x = (-u_xlat16_39) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_19.x = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_19.x;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat16_39 + 1.0;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat38;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_19.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_0 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_17.xyz, u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_0.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_39 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_39 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_39 = max(u_xlat16_39, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_39 = log2(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_39 = exp2(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz * u_xlat4.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_17.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_39 = min(max(u_xlat16_39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_39 = clamp(u_xlat16_39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-u_xlat16_7.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_29 = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat4.x = min(u_xlat16_29, 0.959999979);
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat4.x * _RampTex_ST.x + _RampTex_ST.z;
    u_xlat28 = u_xlat38 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_29 = (-u_xlat38) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_29 = u_xlat16_17.x * u_xlat16_29 + u_xlat28;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x / u_xlat16_29;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_17.x * u_xlat16_39 + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_17.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_17.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_39 = min(max(u_xlat16_39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_39 = clamp(u_xlat16_39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_39 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_17.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_3.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = max(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = min(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss)) * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat4.y = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = texture(_RampTex, u_xlat4.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_5) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * _RampTexColor.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat4.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz / u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = min(u_xlat2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

{

    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_12.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = abs(u_xlat16_35) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_35 = min(u_xlat16_35, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat16_17 = (-u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_35 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = (-u_xlat16_35) + 1.0;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_7.x + u_xlat16_17;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat16_34 / u_xlat36;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_34 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_34 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat36;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat16_33 * u_xlat36;
    u_xlat36 = min(u_xlat36, 100.0);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat16_12.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = clamp(u_xlat36, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat36) + u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat36;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_33 * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_2.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat16_2.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat36;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_3.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot((-u_xlat8.xyz), u_xlat16_12.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x + u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * (-u_xlat16_3.xxx) + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat10_7 = textureCube(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat10_7.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_2.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_7.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz * u_xlat6.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_5.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_2.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat36 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat36) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_2.x + u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_35 / u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_12.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_4.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_4.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_4.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_2.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = max(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = min(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss)) * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat10_0.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = (-u_xlat8.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat6.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat8.zxy) + (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat6.yzx * (-u_xlat8.zxy);
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat8.yzx) * u_xlat6.zxy + (-u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat6.x = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat16_12.xyz);
    u_xlat6.z = dot((-u_xlat8.xyz), u_xlat16_12.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat6.y = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat16_12.xyz);
    u_xlat26 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat26 = inversesqrt(u_xlat26);
    u_xlat6.xy = vec2(u_xlat26) * u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10_6.xyz = texture2D(_MatTex, u_xlat6.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_33) * u_xlat10_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * _MatTexColor.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz / u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = min(u_xlat6.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}
