void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat1.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat2.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat1.zxy) + (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat34 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat34);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat1.zxy) * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat1.yzx) * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat34 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat34);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xxx;
    u_xlat3.y = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat3.x = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot((-u_xlat1.xyz), u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = abs(u_xlat16_5.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(u_xlat16_5.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat16_5.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xx * u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_23 = texture(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_0 = vec4(u_xlat16_23) + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_0 = -abs(u_xlat16_0) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0 = min(max(u_xlat16_0, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0 = clamp(u_xlat16_0, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_16 = dot(u_xlat16_0, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_27.x = u_xlat16_2.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_16 + u_xlat16_27.x;
    u_xlat16_16 = max(u_xlat16_16, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_16 = min(u_xlat16_16, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_27.x = (-u_xlat16_16) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_27.x = u_xlat16_27.x * u_xlat16_16;
    u_xlat23 = u_xlat16_16 + 1.0;
    u_xlat23 = u_xlat23 * u_xlat23;
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_27.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_1.xyw = textureLod(_MatcapTex, u_xlat1.xy, u_xlat16_16).xyz;
    u_xlat35 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat35 = min(max(u_xlat35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat35 = clamp(u_xlat35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(vs_TEXCOORD7.xy,vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
    u_xlat16_3 = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_16 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_3 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_16;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb3 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb3 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb14 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb14 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb3 = u_xlatb14 || u_xlatb3;
    u_xlat16_16 = (u_xlatb3) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_16;
    u_xlat16_27.x = u_xlat35 * u_xlat16_16;
    u_xlat16_27.x = u_xlat16_27.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyw * u_xlat16_27.xxx;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * _MatcapColor.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_4.y * u_xlat16_4.y;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat16_4.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + u_xlat12;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat12);
    u_xlat1.y = u_xlat1.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat34 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_27.xy = max(u_xlat1.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_27.xy = u_xlat16_27.xy * vec2(_SHScale);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_27.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_27.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_27.x = dot(u_xlat16_0, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_37 + u_xlat16_27.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_37 = min(max(u_xlat16_37, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_37 = clamp(u_xlat16_37, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat1.xyw = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * u_xlat1.xyw + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat16_9.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_37) + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat35) * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_16 + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_37 = min(max(u_xlat16_37, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_37 = clamp(u_xlat16_37, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_16) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat1.xyw + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat23 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_37 = (-u_xlat23) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_37 + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_5.x / u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.xzw = u_xlat16_5.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_5.xzw, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_37 * u_xlat16_4.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_15.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_4.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_16 * u_xlat16_15.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_9.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss)) * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz / u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = min(u_xlat1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];

attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;

attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;

vec4 u_xlat0;

vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat1.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;

    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

mediump float u_xlat16_34;

void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, vs_TEXCOORD7.xy).x;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat0.x<vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 0.0 : _MainLightShadowParams.x;
    u_xlat16_11.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x + u_xlat16_11.x;
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
    u_xlatb10 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb10 || u_xlatb0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_1.x + _SHshadow;
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat10_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_12.xy = u_xlat16_12.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_12.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.x = dot(u_xlat16_12.xyz, u_xlat16_12.xyz);
    u_xlat16_13.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_13.x);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xxx;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_12.y * u_xlat16_12.y;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat16_12.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat20 = u_xlat0.x * 0.125 + u_xlat10;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat10);
    u_xlat0.y = u_xlat0.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat20 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_13.xy = max(u_xlat0.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_13.xy = u_xlat16_13.xy * vec2(_SHScale);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_13.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat10_0.x = texture2D(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat10_0.xxxx + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_0 = -abs(u_xlat16_0) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
    u_xlat16_0 = clamp(u_xlat16_0, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_0, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x + u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_0, _roughv4);
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = (-u_xlat16_5.xyz) * u_xlat16_3.xxx + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat16_12.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = clamp(u_xlat36, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat36;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_3.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_3.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = max(u_xlat36, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat8.xyz = (-u_xlat7.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat8.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat7.zxy) + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat7.zxy) * u_xlat8.yzx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat7.yzx) * u_xlat8.zxy + (-u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat8.x = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat16_12.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat8.y = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat16_12.xyz);
    u_xlat8.z = dot((-u_xlat7.xyz), u_xlat16_12.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(u_xlat16_12.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = abs(u_xlat16_3.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat7.xy = vec2(u_xlat36) * u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat7.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat10_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_34 + u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_3.y = max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = min(u_xlat16_3.xy, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_23 = (-u_xlat16_3.y) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_23 * u_xlat16_3.y;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat16_3.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat36;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_23 * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_7.xyz = texture2D(_MatcapTex, u_xlat7.xy, u_xlat16_13.x).xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat10_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * _MatcapColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat6.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_13.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_13.x);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.x = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, u_xlat16_12.xyz);
    u_xlat16_12.x = clamp(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_22 = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_32 = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat6.x = min(u_xlat16_32, 0.959999979);
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat6.x * _RampTex_ST.x + _RampTex_ST.z;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat36 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_32 = (-u_xlat36) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_32 = u_xlat16_22 * u_xlat16_32 + u_xlat26;
    u_xlat16_22 = u_xlat16_22 / u_xlat16_32;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_22 * u_xlat16_12.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_22 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_22 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_22;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_22 * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = clamp(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_22 = u_xlat16_12.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_22;
    u_xlat16_22 = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_22 + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_5.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = max(u_xlat16_12.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = min(u_xlat16_12.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss)) * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat10_0.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat6.y = 0.0;
    u_xlat10_6.xyz = texture2D(_RampTex, u_xlat6.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat10_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * _RampTexColor.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat7.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz / u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = min(u_xlat6.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat1.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Rimlightoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color3;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _metalv4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _roughv4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _MatcapTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ColorTex;
in mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
bool u_xlatb2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
float u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
float u_xlat20;
float u_xlat22;
mediump float u_xlat16_23;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
mediump float u_xlat16_30;
bool u_xlatb30;
float u_xlat32;
mediump float u_xlat16_33;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(vs_TEXCOORD7.xy,vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
    u_xlat16_30 = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_1.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_30 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb30 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb30 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb2 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb2 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb30 = u_xlatb30 || u_xlatb2;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb30) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_1.x + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_13.xy = u_xlat16_13.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_13.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.x = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, u_xlat16_13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_14.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_14.x);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat16_14.xxx;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_13.y * u_xlat16_13.y;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat16_13.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat20 = u_xlat0.x * 0.125 + u_xlat10;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat10);
    u_xlat0.y = u_xlat0.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat20 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_14.xy = max(u_xlat0.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_14.xy = u_xlat16_14.xy * vec2(_SHScale);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_14.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0.xxxx + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_0 = -abs(u_xlat16_0) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0 = min(max(u_xlat16_0, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0 = clamp(u_xlat16_0, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_0, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x + u_xlat16_5.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_0, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat2.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-u_xlat16_6.xyz) * u_xlat16_4.xxx + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat32 = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat32 = min(max(u_xlat32, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat32 = clamp(u_xlat32, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat32) * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat32;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat32 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = max(u_xlat32, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat32 = inversesqrt(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat32) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = (-u_xlat7.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat8.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat7.zxy) + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = inversesqrt(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat32) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat7.zxy) * u_xlat8.yzx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat7.yzx) * u_xlat8.zxy + (-u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat8.x = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat16_13.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = inversesqrt(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat32) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat8.y = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat16_13.xyz);
    u_xlat8.z = dot((-u_xlat7.xyz), u_xlat16_13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = abs(u_xlat16_4.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat32 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = inversesqrt(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat7.xy = vec2(u_xlat32) * u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat7.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_35 + u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat16_4.y = max(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_4.xy = min(u_xlat16_4.xy, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_24 = (-u_xlat16_4.y) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 * u_xlat16_4.y;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat16_4.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat32 * u_xlat32;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_24 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = textureLod(_MatcapTex, u_xlat7.xy, u_xlat16_14.x).xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * _MatcapColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_14.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_14.x);
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.x = dot(u_xlat16_14.xyz, u_xlat16_13.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_23 = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat2.x = min(u_xlat16_33, 0.959999979);
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * _RampTex_ST.x + _RampTex_ST.z;
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat32 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_33 = (-u_xlat32) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_23 * u_xlat16_33 + u_xlat22;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_23 / u_xlat16_33;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_23 * u_xlat16_13.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_23 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_23 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_23;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_23 * u_xlat16_13.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_13.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_23;
    u_xlat16_23 = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_23 + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_6.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = max(u_xlat16_13.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = min(u_xlat16_13.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss)) * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.y = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = texture(_RampTex, u_xlat2.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * _RampTexColor.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat7.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz / u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = min(u_xlat2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

SubProgram "gles " {
Keywords { "_MAIN_LIGHT_SHADOWS" "_SHTYPE_LERP" }

#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[20];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat1.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 100

#ifdef GL_FRAGMENT_PRECISION_HIGH
    precision highp float;
#else
    precision mediump float;
#endif
precision highp int;
uniform 	vec4 _MainLightPosition;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightColor;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightShadowParams;
uniform 	mediump float _NormalScale;
uniform 	mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
uniform 	mediump float _MetallicOffset;
uniform 	mediump float _Emiss;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _EmissColor;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MatcapColor;
uniform 	mediump float _SHScale;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
uniform 	mediump float _SHshadow;
uniform 	mediump vec3 _RimLightDir;
uniform 	mediump float _RimlightScale;
uniform 	mediump float _RimlightScale2;

uniform 	mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _color1;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _color2;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _color3;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _color4;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _metalv4;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _roughv4;

uniform lowp sampler2D _MatcapTex;
varying mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
bool u_xlatb3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
vec3 u_xlat12;
bool u_xlatb12;
bool u_xlatb14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
mediump float u_xlat16_16;
float u_xlat23;
lowp float u_xlat10_23;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_27;
float u_xlat34;
float u_xlat35;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat1.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat2.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat1.zxy) + (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat34 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat34);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat1.zxy) * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat1.yzx) * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat34 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat34);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat10_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xxx;
    u_xlat3.y = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat3.x = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot((-u_xlat1.xyz), u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = abs(u_xlat16_5.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(u_xlat16_5.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat16_5.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xx * u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10_23 = texture2D(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_0 = vec4(u_xlat10_23) + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_0 = -abs(u_xlat16_0) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
    u_xlat16_0 = clamp(u_xlat16_0, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_16 = dot(u_xlat16_0, _roughv4);
    u_xlat10_2 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_27.x = u_xlat10_2.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_16 + u_xlat16_27.x;
    u_xlat16_16 = max(u_xlat16_16, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_16 = min(u_xlat16_16, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_27.x = (-u_xlat16_16) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_27.x = u_xlat16_27.x * u_xlat16_16;
    u_xlat23 = u_xlat16_16 + 1.0;
    u_xlat23 = u_xlat23 * u_xlat23;
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_27.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_1.xyw = texture2D(_MatcapTex, u_xlat1.xy, u_xlat16_16).xyz;
    u_xlat35 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat35 = clamp(u_xlat35, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat3.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, vs_TEXCOORD7.xy).x;
    u_xlatb3 = u_xlat3.x<vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
    u_xlat16_16 = (u_xlatb3) ? 0.0 : _MainLightShadowParams.x;
    u_xlat16_27.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_16 + u_xlat16_27.x;
    u_xlatb3 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
    u_xlatb14 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
    u_xlatb3 = u_xlatb14 || u_xlatb3;
    u_xlat16_16 = (u_xlatb3) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_16;
    u_xlat16_27.x = u_xlat35 * u_xlat16_16;
    u_xlat16_27.x = u_xlat16_27.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyw * u_xlat16_27.xxx;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * _MatcapColor.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_4.y * u_xlat16_4.y;
    u_xlat12.x = u_xlat16_4.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + u_xlat12.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat12.x);
    u_xlat1.y = u_xlat1.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat34 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_27.xy = max(u_xlat1.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_27.xy = u_xlat16_27.xy * vec2(_SHScale);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_27.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_27.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_27.x = dot(u_xlat16_0, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_37 + u_xlat16_27.x;
    u_xlat16_37 = clamp(u_xlat16_37, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat10_2.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = u_xlat10_2.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat1.xyw = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * u_xlat1.xyw + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat16_9.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_37) + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat35) * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_16 + _SHshadow;
    u_xlat16_37 = clamp(u_xlat16_37, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_16) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat1.xyw + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat23 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_37 = (-u_xlat23) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_37 + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_5.x / u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.xzw = u_xlat16_5.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_5.xzw, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_37 * u_xlat16_4.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_15.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_4.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_16 * u_xlat16_15.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_9.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat10_1.xy = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat10_1.yyy * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat10_2.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat12.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat12.xyz / u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = min(u_xlat12.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat12.xyz;
    u_xlatb12 = _BlendMode==0.0;
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb12) ? 1.0 : u_xlat10_1.x;
    return;
}

#endif
"

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat1.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 300 es
#ifdef GL_EXT_shader_texture_lod
#extension GL_EXT_shader_texture_lod : enable
#endif

precision highp float;
precision highp int;
#define HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS 1
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
#define UNITY_UNIFORM
#else
#define UNITY_UNIFORM uniform
#endif
#define UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION 1
#if UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x) layout(location = x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(binding = x, std140)
#else
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)
#endif
uniform 	vec4 _MainLightPosition;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightColor;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightShadowParams;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _NormalScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SpecularColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MetallicOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AOScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Emiss;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _EmissColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MatcapColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHshadow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec3 _AddLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightDarkcolor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightLerp;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec3 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Rimlightoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color3;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _metalv4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _roughv4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _BlendMode;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MatcapTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ColorTex;
in mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
mediump float u_xlat16_3;
bool u_xlatb3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
vec3 u_xlat12;
bool u_xlatb12;
bool u_xlatb14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
mediump float u_xlat16_16;
float u_xlat23;
mediump float u_xlat16_23;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_27;
float u_xlat34;
float u_xlat35;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat1.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat2.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat1.zxy) + (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat34 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat34);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat1.zxy) * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat1.yzx) * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat34 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat34);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xxx;
    u_xlat3.y = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat3.x = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot((-u_xlat1.xyz), u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = abs(u_xlat16_5.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(u_xlat16_5.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat16_5.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xx * u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_23 = texture(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_0 = vec4(u_xlat16_23) + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_0 = -abs(u_xlat16_0) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0 = min(max(u_xlat16_0, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0 = clamp(u_xlat16_0, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_16 = dot(u_xlat16_0, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_27.x = u_xlat16_2.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_16 + u_xlat16_27.x;
    u_xlat16_16 = max(u_xlat16_16, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_16 = min(u_xlat16_16, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_27.x = (-u_xlat16_16) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_27.x = u_xlat16_27.x * u_xlat16_16;
    u_xlat23 = u_xlat16_16 + 1.0;
    u_xlat23 = u_xlat23 * u_xlat23;
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_27.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_1.xyw = textureLod(_MatcapTex, u_xlat1.xy, u_xlat16_16).xyz;
    u_xlat35 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat35 = min(max(u_xlat35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat35 = clamp(u_xlat35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(vs_TEXCOORD7.xy,vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
    u_xlat16_3 = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_16 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_3 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_16;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb3 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb3 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb14 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb14 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb3 = u_xlatb14 || u_xlatb3;
    u_xlat16_16 = (u_xlatb3) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_16;
    u_xlat16_27.x = u_xlat35 * u_xlat16_16;
    u_xlat16_27.x = u_xlat16_27.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyw * u_xlat16_27.xxx;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * _MatcapColor.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_4.y * u_xlat16_4.y;
    u_xlat12.x = u_xlat16_4.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + u_xlat12.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat12.x);
    u_xlat1.y = u_xlat1.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat34 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_27.xy = max(u_xlat1.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_27.xy = u_xlat16_27.xy * vec2(_SHScale);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_27.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_27.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_27.x = dot(u_xlat16_0, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_37 + u_xlat16_27.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_37 = min(max(u_xlat16_37, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_37 = clamp(u_xlat16_37, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat1.xyw = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * u_xlat1.xyw + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat16_9.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_37) + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat35) * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_16 + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_37 = min(max(u_xlat16_37, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_37 = clamp(u_xlat16_37, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_16) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat1.xyw + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat23 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_37 = (-u_xlat23) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_37 + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_5.x / u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.xzw = u_xlat16_5.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_5.xzw, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_37 * u_xlat16_4.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_15.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_4.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_16 * u_xlat16_15.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_9.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xy = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat12.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat12.xyz / u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = min(u_xlat12.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat12.xyz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb12 = !!(_BlendMode==0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb12 = _BlendMode==0.0;
#endif
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb12) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}
SubProgram "gles " {
Keywords { "_MAIN_LIGHT_SHADOWS" "_SHTYPE_LERP" }
Local Keywords { "_BUMP_ON" "_COLOR_MASK" "_DEBUG_OFF" "_IFRAMP_ON" "_MATCAPENV_ON" "_Mask_ON" }
"// hash: ac164931de38dd9e
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[20];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat1.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT

    precision highp float;

precision highp int;
uniform 	vec4 _MainLightPosition;

varying mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;

varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
lowp vec3 u_xlat10_6;
bool u_xlatb6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
lowp vec3 u_xlat10_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;

float u_xlat10;
bool u_xlatb10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;

mediump float u_xlat16_22;
mediump float u_xlat16_23;

mediump float u_xlat16_34;
float u_xlat36;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, vs_TEXCOORD7.xy).x;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat0.x<vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 0.0 : _MainLightShadowParams.x;
    u_xlat16_11.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x + u_xlat16_11.x;
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
    u_xlatb10 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb10 || u_xlatb0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_1.x + _SHshadow;
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat10_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_12.xy = u_xlat16_12.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_12.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.x = dot(u_xlat16_12.xyz, u_xlat16_12.xyz);
    u_xlat16_13.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_13.x);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xxx;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_12.y * u_xlat16_12.y;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat16_12.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat20 = u_xlat0.x * 0.125 + u_xlat10;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat10);
    u_xlat0.y = u_xlat0.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat20 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_13.xy = max(u_xlat0.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_13.xy = u_xlat16_13.xy * vec2(_SHScale);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_13.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat10_0.x = texture2D(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat10_0.xxxx + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_0 = -abs(u_xlat16_0) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
    u_xlat16_0 = clamp(u_xlat16_0, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_0, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x + u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_0, _roughv4);
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = (-u_xlat16_5.xyz) * u_xlat16_3.xxx + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat16_12.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = clamp(u_xlat36, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat36;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_3.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_3.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = max(u_xlat36, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat8.xyz = (-u_xlat7.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat8.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat7.zxy) + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat7.zxy) * u_xlat8.yzx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat7.yzx) * u_xlat8.zxy + (-u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat8.x = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat16_12.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat8.y = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat16_12.xyz);
    u_xlat8.z = dot((-u_xlat7.xyz), u_xlat16_12.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(u_xlat16_12.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = abs(u_xlat16_3.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat7.xy = vec2(u_xlat36) * u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat7.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat10_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_34 + u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_3.y = max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = min(u_xlat16_3.xy, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_23 = (-u_xlat16_3.y) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_23 * u_xlat16_3.y;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat16_3.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat36;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_23 * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_7.xyz = texture2D(_MatcapTex, u_xlat7.xy, u_xlat16_13.x).xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat10_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * _MatcapColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat6.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_13.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_13.x);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.x = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, u_xlat16_12.xyz);
    u_xlat16_12.x = clamp(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_22 = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_32 = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat6.x = min(u_xlat16_32, 0.959999979);
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat6.x * _RampTex_ST.x + _RampTex_ST.z;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat36 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_32 = (-u_xlat36) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_32 = u_xlat16_22 * u_xlat16_32 + u_xlat26;
    u_xlat16_22 = u_xlat16_22 / u_xlat16_32;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_22 * u_xlat16_12.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_22 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_22 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_22;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_22 * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = clamp(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_22 = u_xlat16_12.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_22;
    u_xlat16_22 = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_22 + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_5.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = max(u_xlat16_12.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = min(u_xlat16_12.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat10_7.xyz = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat10_7.zzz * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat10_0.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat6.y = 0.0;
    u_xlat10_6.xyz = texture2D(_RampTex, u_xlat6.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat10_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * _RampTexColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat10_7.yyy + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat17.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat17.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat17.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz / u_xlat17.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = min(u_xlat6.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlatb6 = _BlendMode==0.0;
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb6) ? 1.0 : u_xlat10_7.x;
    return;
}

void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat1.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

#endif

precision highp float;

uniform 	vec4 _MainLightPosition;
