#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _MatcapTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _ColorTex;
in mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
bool u_xlatb2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
float u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
vec3 u_xlat17;
float u_xlat20;
float u_xlat22;
mediump float u_xlat16_23;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
mediump float u_xlat16_30;
bool u_xlatb30;
float u_xlat32;
mediump float u_xlat16_33;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(vs_TEXCOORD7.xy,vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
    u_xlat16_30 = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_1.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_30 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb30 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb30 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb2 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb2 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb30 = u_xlatb30 || u_xlatb2;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb30) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_1.x + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_13.xy = u_xlat16_13.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_13.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.x = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, u_xlat16_13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_14.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_14.x);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat16_14.xxx;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_13.y * u_xlat16_13.y;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat16_13.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat20 = u_xlat0.x * 0.125 + u_xlat10;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat10);
    u_xlat0.y = u_xlat0.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat20 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_14.xy = max(u_xlat0.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_14.xy = u_xlat16_14.xy * vec2(_SHScale);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_14.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0.xxxx + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_0 = -abs(u_xlat16_0) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0 = min(max(u_xlat16_0, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0 = clamp(u_xlat16_0, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_0, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x + u_xlat16_5.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_0, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat2.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-u_xlat16_6.xyz) * u_xlat16_4.xxx + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat32 = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat32 = min(max(u_xlat32, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat32 = clamp(u_xlat32, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat32) * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat32;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat32 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = max(u_xlat32, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat32 = inversesqrt(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat32) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = (-u_xlat7.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat8.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat7.zxy) + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = inversesqrt(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat32) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat7.zxy) * u_xlat8.yzx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat7.yzx) * u_xlat8.zxy + (-u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat8.x = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat16_13.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = inversesqrt(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat32) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat8.y = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat16_13.xyz);
    u_xlat8.z = dot((-u_xlat7.xyz), u_xlat16_13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = abs(u_xlat16_4.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat32 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = inversesqrt(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat7.xy = vec2(u_xlat32) * u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat7.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_35 + u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat16_4.y = max(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_4.xy = min(u_xlat16_4.xy, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_24 = (-u_xlat16_4.y) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 * u_xlat16_4.y;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat16_4.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat32 * u_xlat32;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_24 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = textureLod(_MatcapTex, u_xlat7.xy, u_xlat16_14.x).xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * _MatcapColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_14.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_14.x);
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.x = dot(u_xlat16_14.xyz, u_xlat16_13.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_23 = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat2.x = min(u_xlat16_33, 0.959999979);
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * _RampTex_ST.x + _RampTex_ST.z;
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat32 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_33 = (-u_xlat32) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_23 * u_xlat16_33 + u_xlat22;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_23 / u_xlat16_33;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_23 * u_xlat16_13.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_23 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_23 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_23;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_23 * u_xlat16_13.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_13.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_23;
    u_xlat16_23 = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_23 + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_6.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = max(u_xlat16_13.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = min(u_xlat16_13.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_7.zzz * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.y = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = texture(_RampTex, u_xlat2.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * _RampTexColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_7.yyy + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat17.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat17.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat17.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz / u_xlat17.xyz;

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;

{

uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[20];
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(1) uniform UnityPerDraw {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LODFade;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightData;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightIndices[2];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_ProbesOcclusion;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SpecCube0_HDR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_DynamicLightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHC;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _NormalScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SpecularColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MetallicOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AOScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Emiss;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _EmissColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MatTexColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MatcapColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHshadow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec3 _AddLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightDarkcolor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightLerp;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec3 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Rimlightoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color3;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _metalv4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _roughv4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _BlendMode;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat1.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

#endif

precision highp float;
precision highp int;
#define HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS 1
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
#define UNITY_UNIFORM
#else
#define UNITY_UNIFORM uniform
#endif
#define UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION 1
#if UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x) layout(location = x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(binding = x, std140)
#else
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)
#endif
uniform 	vec4 _MainLightPosition;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightColor;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightShadowParams;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _NormalScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SpecularColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MetallicOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AOScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Emiss;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MatTexColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MatcapColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHshadow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec3 _AddLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightDarkcolor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightLerp;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec3 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color3;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _metalv4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _roughv4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _BlendMode;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MatTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _MatcapTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _ColorTex;
in mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
bool u_xlatb2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
float u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
vec3 u_xlat12;
bool u_xlatb12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
float u_xlat20;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
mediump float u_xlat16_30;
bool u_xlatb30;
float u_xlat32;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(vs_TEXCOORD7.xy,vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
    u_xlat16_30 = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_1.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_30 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb30 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb30 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb2 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb2 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb30 = u_xlatb30 || u_xlatb2;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb30) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_1.x + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_13.xy = u_xlat16_13.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_13.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.x = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, u_xlat16_13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_14.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_14.x);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat16_14.xxx;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_13.y * u_xlat16_13.y;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat16_13.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat20 = u_xlat0.x * 0.125 + u_xlat10;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat10);
    u_xlat0.y = u_xlat0.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat20 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_14.xy = max(u_xlat0.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_14.xy = u_xlat16_14.xy * vec2(_SHScale);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_14.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0.xxxx + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_0 = -abs(u_xlat16_0) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0 = min(max(u_xlat16_0, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0 = clamp(u_xlat16_0, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_0, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x + u_xlat16_5.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_0, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat2.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-u_xlat16_6.xyz) * u_xlat16_4.xxx + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat32 = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat32 = min(max(u_xlat32, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat32 = clamp(u_xlat32, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat32) * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat32;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat32 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = max(u_xlat32, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat32 = inversesqrt(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat32) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = (-u_xlat7.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat8.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat7.zxy) + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = inversesqrt(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat32) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat7.zxy) * u_xlat8.yzx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat7.yzx) * u_xlat8.zxy + (-u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat8.x = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat16_13.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = inversesqrt(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat32) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat8.y = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat16_13.xyz);
    u_xlat8.z = dot((-u_xlat7.xyz), u_xlat16_13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = abs(u_xlat16_4.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat32 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = inversesqrt(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat7.xy = vec2(u_xlat32) * u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat7.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_35 + u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat16_14.x = max(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_14.x = min(u_xlat16_14.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_24 = (-u_xlat16_14.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 * u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat16_14.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat32 * u_xlat32;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_24 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = textureLod(_MatcapTex, u_xlat7.xy, u_xlat16_14.x).xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = texture(_MatTex, u_xlat7.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * _MatcapColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * _MatTexColor.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat32 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat32) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_3.x + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_4.x / u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.x = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_13.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_13.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_13.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_13.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_3.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_13.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_6.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = max(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = min(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.zzz * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * u_xlat16_2.yyy + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat7.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat12.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat12.xyz / u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = min(u_xlat12.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat12.xyz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb12 = !!(_BlendMode==0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb12 = _BlendMode==0.0;
#endif
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb12) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_2.x;
    return;
}

#endif
"

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;

vec4 u_xlat0;

void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);

    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat1.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;

    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);

    u_xlat16_7.x = abs(u_xlat16_7.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_7.x = min(u_xlat16_7.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat37 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat37 = inversesqrt(u_xlat37);
    u_xlat5.xy = vec2(u_xlat37) * u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat5.xy = u_xlat5.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat10_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x + u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(u_xlat16_3.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_18.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat33;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_18.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_5.xyz = texture2D(_MatcapTex, u_xlat5.xy, u_xlat16_3.x).xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat10_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * _MatcapColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * u_xlat4.xyz + u_xlat16_14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(u_xlat16_18.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = clamp(u_xlat16_36, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-u_xlat16_7.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17 = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat4.x = min(u_xlat16_17, 0.959999979);
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat4.x * _RampTex_ST.x + _RampTex_ST.z;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat33 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_17 = (-u_xlat33) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17 = u_xlat16_6.x * u_xlat16_17 + u_xlat26;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x / u_xlat16_17;
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_6.x * u_xlat16_36 + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_6.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_36 * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_36 = clamp(u_xlat16_36, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_36 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_36 * u_xlat16_36;
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_36 * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_6.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_36;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_2.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = min(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat10_5.xyz = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_5.zzz * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat10_0.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat4.y = 0.0;
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_RampTex, u_xlat4.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * _RampTexColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat10_5.yyy + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat4.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlatb0 = _BlendMode==0.0;
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat10_5.x;
    return;
}

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;

out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;

out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat1.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;

layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;

mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;

mediump float u_xlat16_35;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
float u_xlat37;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
bool u_xlatb37;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb1 = !!(u_xlat16_0.y>=u_xlat16_0.z);
#else
    u_xlatb1 = u_xlat16_0.y>=u_xlat16_0.z;
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.x = (u_xlatb1) ? 1.0 : 0.0;
    u_xlat16_13.xy = (-u_xlat16_0.zy) + u_xlat16_0.yz;
    u_xlat16_1.xy = u_xlat16_2.xx * u_xlat16_13.xy + u_xlat16_0.zy;
    u_xlat16_13.x = float(1.0);
    u_xlat16_13.y = float(-1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.zw = u_xlat16_2.xx * u_xlat16_13.xy + vec2(-1.0, 0.666666687);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = (-u_xlat16_1.xyw);
    u_xlat16_2.w = (-u_xlat16_0.x);
    u_xlat16_3.yzw = u_xlat16_1.yzx + u_xlat16_2.yzw;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_0.x + u_xlat16_2.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb4 = !!(u_xlat16_0.x>=u_xlat16_1.x);
#else
    u_xlatb4 = u_xlat16_0.x>=u_xlat16_1.x;
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.x = (u_xlatb4) ? 1.0 : 0.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_3.w + u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xzw = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyw;
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(u_xlat16_2.z, u_xlat16_13.x);
    u_xlat16_13.x = (-u_xlat16_2.z) + u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_2.x + (-u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_24 * 6.0 + 1.00000001e-07;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x / u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x + u_xlat16_2.w;
    u_xlat16_13.x = abs(u_xlat16_13.x) + _ColorHUE;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xxx * vec3(6.0, 6.0, 6.0) + vec3(-3.0, -2.0, -4.0);
    u_xlat4.xyz = abs(u_xlat4.xyz) * vec3(1.0, -1.0, -1.0) + vec3(-1.0, 2.0, 2.0);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat4.xyz = min(max(u_xlat4.xyz, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat4.xyz = clamp(u_xlat4.xyz, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_2.x + 1.00000001e-07;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_24 / u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x + _ColorSaturation;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xxx + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_37 = texture(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_1 = vec4(u_xlat16_37) + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_1 = -abs(u_xlat16_1) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1 = min(max(u_xlat16_1, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1 = clamp(u_xlat16_1, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_1, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(u_xlat16_1, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_1.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 + u_xlat16_14.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat5.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = (-u_xlat16_2.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_35) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xy = u_xlat16_6.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyw = u_xlat16_6.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyw;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat37 = u_xlat16_6.y * u_xlat16_6.y;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_6.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat16 = u_xlat37 * 0.125 + u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat37 = u_xlat37 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat5.x);
    u_xlat8.y = u_xlat37 + 0.125;
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat16 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_7.xy = max(u_xlat8.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xy = u_xlat16_7.xy * vec2(_SHScale);
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_7.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(vs_TEXCOORD7.xy,vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
    u_xlat16_37 = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_35 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_37 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_35;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb37 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb37 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb5 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb5 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb37 = u_xlatb37 || u_xlatb5;
    u_xlat16_35 = (u_xlatb37) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_35 + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_39 = min(max(u_xlat16_39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_39 = clamp(u_xlat16_39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat37 = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat37 = min(max(u_xlat37, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat37 = clamp(u_xlat37, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * vec3(u_xlat37);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat37;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_7.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_7.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat37 = dot(u_xlat16_7.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
    u_xlat37 = max(u_xlat37, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat37 = inversesqrt(u_xlat37);
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat37) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = (-u_xlat5.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat8.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat5.zxy) + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat37 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat37 = inversesqrt(u_xlat37);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat37) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = (-u_xlat5.zxy) * u_xlat8.yzx;
    u_xlat10.xyz = (-u_xlat5.yzx) * u_xlat8.zxy + (-u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat8.x = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat37 = dot(u_xlat10.xyz, u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat37 = inversesqrt(u_xlat37);
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat37) * u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat8.y = dot(u_xlat10.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat8.z = dot((-u_xlat5.xyz), u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = abs(u_xlat16_7.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_7.x = min(u_xlat16_7.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat37 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat37 = inversesqrt(u_xlat37);
    u_xlat5.xy = vec2(u_xlat37) * u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat5.xy = u_xlat5.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x + u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(u_xlat16_3.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_18.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat33;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_18.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = textureLod(_MatcapTex, u_xlat5.xy, u_xlat16_3.x).xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * _MatcapColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * u_xlat4.xyz + u_xlat16_14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(u_xlat16_18.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_36 = min(max(u_xlat16_36, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_36 = clamp(u_xlat16_36, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-u_xlat16_7.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17 = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat4.x = min(u_xlat16_17, 0.959999979);
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat4.x * _RampTex_ST.x + _RampTex_ST.z;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat33 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_17 = (-u_xlat33) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17 = u_xlat16_6.x * u_xlat16_17 + u_xlat26;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x / u_xlat16_17;
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_6.x * u_xlat16_36 + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_6.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_36 * u_xlat16_6.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_36 = min(max(u_xlat16_36, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_36 = clamp(u_xlat16_36, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_36 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_36 * u_xlat16_36;
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_36 * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_6.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_36;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_2.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = min(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_5.zzz * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat4.y = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_RampTex, u_xlat4.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * _RampTexColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_5.yyy + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat4.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;

    u_xlatb0 = !!(_BlendMode==0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = _BlendMode==0.0;
#endif
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_5.x;
    return;

#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];

uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat1.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

mediump float u_xlat16_42;
float u_xlat44;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, vs_TEXCOORD7.xy).x;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat0.x<vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 0.0 : _MainLightShadowParams.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x + u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
    u_xlatb12 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb12 || u_xlatb0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat10_0.x = texture2D(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat10_0.xxxx + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_0 = -abs(u_xlat16_0) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);

    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;

    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat10_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_38 = dot(u_xlat16_0, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_5 = dot(u_xlat16_0, _roughv4);

    u_xlat16_38 = clamp(u_xlat16_38, 0.0, 1.0);

    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_5 + u_xlat16_38;

    u_xlat16_38 = min(u_xlat16_38, 1.0);

    u_xlat16_7.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_7.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;

    u_xlat39 = max(u_xlat39, 1.17549435e-38);

    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;

    u_xlat16_7.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_7.x);

    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);

    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 * u_xlat16_42 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_42;

    u_xlat39 = u_xlat39 * u_xlat16_5;
    u_xlat39 = min(u_xlat39, 100.0);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat39) * u_xlat4.xyz;

    u_xlat39 = clamp(u_xlat39, 0.0, 1.0);

    u_xlat40 = u_xlat16_6.y * 0.25;

    u_xlat39 = u_xlat39 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat40);

    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat44 + 0.125;

    u_xlat16_17.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_10) * u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_19.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xyz + u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.x = dot((-u_xlat8.xyz), u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x + u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * (-u_xlat16_17.xxx) + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_19.x = (-u_xlat16_38) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_19.x = u_xlat16_38 * u_xlat16_19.x;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat16_38 + 1.0;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat39 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_19.x * 6.0;

    u_xlat16_38 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_38 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_38 = max(u_xlat16_38, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_38 = log2(u_xlat16_38);

    u_xlat16_38 = exp2(u_xlat16_38);

    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz * u_xlat4.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;

    u_xlat16_29 = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat4.x = min(u_xlat16_29, 0.959999979);
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat4.x * _RampTex_ST.x + _RampTex_ST.z;
    u_xlat28 = u_xlat39 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_29 = (-u_xlat39) * 0.125 + 1.0;

    u_xlat16_17.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_17.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_38 = clamp(u_xlat16_38, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_38 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * u_xlat16_38;
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_17.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_38;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_2.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = min(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;

    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat10_3.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat4.y = 0.0;
    u_xlat10_3.xyz = texture2D(_RampTex, u_xlat4.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_5) * u_xlat10_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * _RampTexColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat10_8.yyy + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);

    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);

    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz / u_xlat4.xyz;

    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlatb3 = _BlendMode==0.0;
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb3) ? 1.0 : u_xlat10_8.x;
    return;

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;

out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;

out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat1.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat0;

#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)

uniform 	vec4 _MainLightPosition;

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;

UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _ColorTex;
in mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
bool u_xlatb2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
mediump float u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump float u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_17;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_19;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_22;
float u_xlat28;
mediump float u_xlat16_29;
mediump float u_xlat16_31;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
bool u_xlatb36;
float u_xlat38;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
float u_xlat40;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
float u_xlat44;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(vs_TEXCOORD7.xy,vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
    u_xlat16_36 = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_1.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_36 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb36 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb36 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb2 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb2 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb36 = u_xlatb36 || u_xlatb2;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb36) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0.xxxx + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_0 = -abs(u_xlat16_0) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0 = min(max(u_xlat16_0, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0 = clamp(u_xlat16_0, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_0, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_5 = dot(u_xlat16_0, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 + u_xlat16_17.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_39 = min(max(u_xlat16_39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_39 = clamp(u_xlat16_39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat4.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = (-u_xlat16_3.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_39) + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_2.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_5 + u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_39 = max(u_xlat16_39, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_39 = min(u_xlat16_39, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_5 = u_xlat16_39 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_7.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_7.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_7.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat38 = dot(u_xlat16_7.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
    u_xlat38 = max(u_xlat38, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat38 = inversesqrt(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat38) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xy = u_xlat16_6.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_7.x);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xxx;
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = abs(u_xlat16_7.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_7.x = min(u_xlat16_7.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_19.x = u_xlat16_42 * u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat16_31 = (-u_xlat16_7.x) * u_xlat16_7.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat16_19.x * u_xlat16_19.x + u_xlat16_31;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat16_42 / u_xlat38;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 * u_xlat16_42 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat38;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat16_5;
    u_xlat38 = min(u_xlat38, 100.0);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat38) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat38 = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat38 = min(max(u_xlat38, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat38 = clamp(u_xlat38, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat38) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_19.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * vec3(u_xlat38) + u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5 = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat38;
    u_xlat16_5 = u_xlat16_5 * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_10 = u_xlat16_1.x + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_10 = min(max(u_xlat16_10, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_10 = clamp(u_xlat16_10, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat16_6.y * u_xlat16_6.y;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat16_6.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat44 = u_xlat38 * 0.125 + u_xlat40;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat40);
    u_xlat9.y = u_xlat38 + 0.125;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat44 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_22.xy = max(u_xlat9.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_22.xy = u_xlat16_22.xy * vec2(_SHScale);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_22.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_10) * u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_19.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xyz + u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.x = dot((-u_xlat8.xyz), u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x + u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * (-u_xlat16_17.xxx) + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_19.x = (-u_xlat16_39) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_19.x = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_19.x;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat16_39 + 1.0;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat38;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_19.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_0 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_17.xyz, u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_0.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_39 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_39 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_39 = max(u_xlat16_39, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_39 = log2(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_39 = exp2(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz * u_xlat4.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_17.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_39 = min(max(u_xlat16_39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_39 = clamp(u_xlat16_39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-u_xlat16_7.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_29 = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat4.x = min(u_xlat16_29, 0.959999979);
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat4.x * _RampTex_ST.x + _RampTex_ST.z;
    u_xlat28 = u_xlat38 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_29 = (-u_xlat38) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_29 = u_xlat16_17.x * u_xlat16_29 + u_xlat28;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x / u_xlat16_29;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_17.x * u_xlat16_39 + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_17.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_17.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_39 = min(max(u_xlat16_39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_39 = clamp(u_xlat16_39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_39 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_17.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_3.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = max(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = min(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_8.zzz * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat4.y = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = texture(_RampTex, u_xlat4.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_5) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * _RampTexColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_8.yyy + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat4.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz / u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = min(u_xlat2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb2 = !!(_BlendMode==0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb2 = _BlendMode==0.0;
#endif
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb2) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_8.x;
    return;
}

#endif

SubProgram "gles " {
Keywords { "_ADDITIONAL_LIGHTS" "_MAIN_LIGHT_SHADOWS" "_SHTYPE_LERP" }
Local Keywords { "_BUMP_ON" "_DEBUG_OFF" }
"// hash: 9769df2bba8bcb5
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[20];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}
