UNITY_BINDING(1) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _NormalScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SpecularColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MetallicOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AOScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Emiss;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _EmissColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MatTexColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHshadow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec3 _AddLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightDarkcolor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightLerp;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec3 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Rimlightoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color3;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _metalv4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _roughv4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _MatTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ColorTex;
in mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
vec3 u_xlat11;
vec3 u_xlat12;
vec3 u_xlat13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
uint u_xlatu16;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_19;
float u_xlat24;
float u_xlat32;
int u_xlati32;
bool u_xlatb32;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_35;
float u_xlat48;
mediump float u_xlat16_48;
bool u_xlatb48;
mediump float u_xlat16_50;
mediump float u_xlat16_51;
mediump float u_xlat16_52;
mediump float u_xlat16_53;
float u_xlat56;
bool u_xlatb56;
float u_xlat57;
float u_xlat58;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_1.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_48 = texture(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_1 = vec4(u_xlat16_48) + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_1 = -abs(u_xlat16_1) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1 = min(max(u_xlat16_1, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1 = clamp(u_xlat16_1, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_19.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_19.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_19.xyz;
    u_xlat16_19.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_19.xyz;
    u_xlat16_19.xyz = u_xlat16_1.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_19.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_19.xyz;
    u_xlat16_52 = dot(u_xlat16_1, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 + u_xlat16_52;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_50 = min(max(u_xlat16_50, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_50 = clamp(u_xlat16_50, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_52 = dot(u_xlat16_1, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x + u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss)) * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(u_xlat16_3.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-u_xlat16_4.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_50) + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_7.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_7.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat16_7.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
    u_xlat48 = max(u_xlat48, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat48 = inversesqrt(u_xlat48);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat48) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_2.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_52 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_52 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_52);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_52);
    u_xlat9.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(vs_TEXCOORD7.xy,vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
    u_xlat16_48 = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_52 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_48 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_52;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb48 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb48 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb56 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb56 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb48 = u_xlatb48 || u_xlatb56;
    u_xlat16_52 = (u_xlatb48) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_19.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_50) * u_xlat10.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat48 = min(max(u_xlat48, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat48 = clamp(u_xlat48, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_19.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_19.x = abs(u_xlat16_19.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_19.x = min(u_xlat16_19.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat56 = u_xlat16_2.y * u_xlat16_2.y;
    u_xlat57 = u_xlat16_2.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat58 = u_xlat56 * 0.125 + u_xlat57;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat58 + 0.125;
    u_xlat56 = u_xlat56 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat57);
    u_xlat11.y = u_xlat56 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_35.xy = max(u_xlat11.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_35.xy = u_xlat16_35.xy * vec2(_SHScale);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_35.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_35.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35.x = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat48;
    u_xlat16_35.x = u_xlat16_35.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat11.xyz = (-u_xlat8.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat11.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat8.zxy) + (-u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat56 = dot(u_xlat11.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat56 = inversesqrt(u_xlat56);
    u_xlat11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat56) * u_xlat11.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = (-u_xlat8.zxy) * u_xlat11.yzx;
    u_xlat12.xyz = (-u_xlat8.yzx) * u_xlat11.zxy + (-u_xlat12.xyz);
    u_xlat56 = dot(u_xlat12.xyz, u_xlat12.xyz);
    u_xlat56 = inversesqrt(u_xlat56);
    u_xlat12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat56) * u_xlat12.xyz;
    u_xlat11.x = dot(u_xlat11.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat11.y = dot(u_xlat12.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat11.z = dot((-u_xlat8.xyz), u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat56 = dot(u_xlat11.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat56 = inversesqrt(u_xlat56);
    u_xlat11.xy = vec2(u_xlat56) * u_xlat11.xy;
    u_xlat11.xy = u_xlat11.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_51 = (-u_xlat16_19.x) * u_xlat16_19.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_53 = u_xlat16_50 * u_xlat16_19.x;
    u_xlat56 = u_xlat16_53 * u_xlat16_53 + u_xlat16_51;
    u_xlat56 = u_xlat16_50 / u_xlat56;
    u_xlat56 = u_xlat56 * u_xlat56;
    u_xlat16_51 = u_xlat16_3.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat56 = u_xlat56 * u_xlat16_51;
    u_xlat56 = min(u_xlat56, 100.0);
    u_xlat12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat56) * u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat48) * u_xlat12.xyz;
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat13.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_51 = dot((-u_xlat8.xyz), u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_51 = u_xlat16_51 + u_xlat16_51;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_51)) + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_51 = (-u_xlat16_3.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_51 = u_xlat16_51 * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_51 = u_xlat16_51 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_1 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_14.xyz, u_xlat16_51);
    u_xlat16_51 = u_xlat16_1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_51 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_51 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_51 = max(u_xlat16_51, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_51 = log2(u_xlat16_51);
    u_xlat16_51 = u_xlat16_51 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_51 = exp2(u_xlat16_51);
    u_xlat16_51 = u_xlat16_51 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_51);
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 * u_xlat16_50 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_50 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_50;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_50);
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_52) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(u_xlat48) + u_xlat13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_52 + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_50 = min(max(u_xlat16_50, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_50 = clamp(u_xlat16_50, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_50) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * u_xlat16_14.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz * u_xlat10.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_50 = (-u_xlat16_19.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat8.x * u_xlat8.x;
    u_xlat24 = u_xlat8.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat8.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_50 * u_xlat16_3.x + u_xlat24;
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 / u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyw, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_19.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 * u_xlat16_3.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_3.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_19.x;
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 * u_xlat16_3.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_50 = min(max(u_xlat16_50, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_50 = clamp(u_xlat16_50, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_50 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 * u_xlat16_50;
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_3.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_4.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_4.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = vec3(u_xlat16_50) * u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = max(u_xlat16_3.xyw, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = min(u_xlat16_3.xyw, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xyw + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_MatTex, u_xlat11.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_35.xxx * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * _MatTexColor.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_50 = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlatu0 = uint(int(u_xlat16_50));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat12.xyz * vec3(u_xlat48) + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    for(uint u_xlatu_loop_1 = uint(0u) ; u_xlatu_loop_1<u_xlatu0 ; u_xlatu_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat32 = float(int(u_xlatu_loop_1));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb48 = !!(u_xlat32<2.0);
#else
        u_xlatb48 = u_xlat32<2.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_6.xy = (bool(u_xlatb48)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat8.x = u_xlat32 + -2.0;
        u_xlat32 = (u_xlatb48) ? u_xlat32 : u_xlat8.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb32 = !!(u_xlat32<1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb32 = u_xlat32<1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_50 = (u_xlatb32) ? u_xlat16_6.x : u_xlat16_6.y;
        u_xlati32 = int(u_xlat16_50);
        u_xlat8.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPosition[u_xlati32].xyz;
        u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
        u_xlat48 = max(u_xlat48, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat56 = inversesqrt(u_xlat48);
        u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat56) * u_xlat8.xyz;
        u_xlat56 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat48);
        u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati32].x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati32].y;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat48 = min(max(u_xlat48, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat48 = clamp(u_xlat48, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat56;
        u_xlat16_50 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDir[u_xlati32].xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
        u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati32].z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati32].w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_50 = min(max(u_xlat16_50, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_50 = clamp(u_xlat16_50, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 * u_xlat16_50;
        u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat16_50;
        u_xlat16_50 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_50 = min(max(u_xlat16_50, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_50 = clamp(u_xlat16_50, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_50) * _AdditionalLightsColor[u_xlati32].xyz;
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat48) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
        u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);

    u_xlat16_31.x = u_xlat16_31.x + u_xlat16_31.x;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * (-u_xlat16_31.xxx) + (-u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_31.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_31.x = u_xlat16_31.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_31.x = u_xlat16_31.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_1 = textureCube(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_12.xyz, u_xlat16_31.x);
    u_xlat16_31.x = u_xlat10_1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_31.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_31.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_31.x = max(u_xlat16_31.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_31.x = log2(u_xlat16_31.x);
    u_xlat16_31.x = u_xlat16_31.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_31.x = exp2(u_xlat16_31.x);
    u_xlat16_31.x = u_xlat16_31.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * u_xlat16_31.xxx;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 * u_xlat16_44 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_44 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_44;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_44);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_46) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(u_xlat42) + u_xlat11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_46 + _SHshadow;
    u_xlat16_44 = clamp(u_xlat16_44, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_44) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat9.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_44 = (-u_xlat16_17.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat1.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_44 * u_xlat16_3.x + u_xlat15;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 / u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 * u_xlat16_3.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_3.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_44 = clamp(u_xlat16_44, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_44 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 * u_xlat16_44;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_46 * u_xlat16_3.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_5.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_44) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = max(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = min(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat10_0.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_44 = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlati0 = int(u_xlat16_44);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz * vec3(u_xlat42) + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    for(int u_xlati_loop_1 = 0 ; u_xlati_loop_1<u_xlati0 ; u_xlati_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat28 = float(u_xlati_loop_1);
        u_xlatb42 = u_xlat28<2.0;
        u_xlat16_6.xy = (bool(u_xlatb42)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat1.x = u_xlat28 + -2.0;
        u_xlat28 = (u_xlatb42) ? u_xlat28 : u_xlat1.x;
        u_xlatb28 = u_xlat28<1.0;
        u_xlat16_44 = (u_xlatb28) ? u_xlat16_6.x : u_xlat16_6.y;
        u_xlati28 = int(u_xlat16_44);
        u_xlat1.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPositionDynamicIndex(u_xlati28).xyz;
        u_xlat42 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat42 = max(u_xlat42, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat43 = inversesqrt(u_xlat42);
        u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat43) * u_xlat1.xyz;
        u_xlat43 = float(1.0) / u_xlat42;
        u_xlat42 = u_xlat42 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati28).x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati28).y;
        u_xlat42 = clamp(u_xlat42, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat42 = u_xlat42 * u_xlat43;
        u_xlat16_44 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDirDynamicIndex(u_xlati28).xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati28).z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati28).w;
        u_xlat16_44 = clamp(u_xlat16_44, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 * u_xlat16_44;
        u_xlat42 = u_xlat42 * u_xlat16_44;
        u_xlat16_44 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_44 = clamp(u_xlat16_44, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_44) * _AdditionalLightsColorDynamicIndex(u_xlati28).xyz;
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat42) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
        u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    return;
}

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;

in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;

vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;

    return;

void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);

    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_1.w + _MetallicOffset;

#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb29 = !!(_BlendMode==0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb29 = _BlendMode==0.0;
#endif
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb29) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;

#else

    u_xlat16_3.x = min(u_xlat16_3.x, 1.0);

    u_xlat16_7.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_7.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_7.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat42 = dot(u_xlat16_7.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
    u_xlat42 = max(u_xlat42, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat42);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat42) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_2.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;

    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_46 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);

    u_xlatb42 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else

#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb43 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb43 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb42 = u_xlatb42 || u_xlatb43;
    u_xlat16_46 = (u_xlatb42) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_46;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_17.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_44) * u_xlat9.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat42 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat42 = min(max(u_xlat42, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat42 = clamp(u_xlat42, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_17.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_17.x = abs(u_xlat16_17.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_17.x = min(u_xlat16_17.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat16_2.y * u_xlat16_2.y;
    u_xlat50 = u_xlat16_2.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat51 = u_xlat43 * 0.125 + u_xlat50;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat51 + 0.125;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat50);
    u_xlat10.y = u_xlat43 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_31.xy = max(u_xlat10.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_31.xy = u_xlat16_31.xy * vec2(_SHScale);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_31.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_31.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;

    u_xlat43 = u_xlat16_45 * u_xlat16_45 + u_xlat16_31.x;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat16_44 / u_xlat43;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 * u_xlat43;
    u_xlat16_31.x = u_xlat16_3.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 * u_xlat16_31.x;
    u_xlat43 = min(u_xlat43, 100.0);
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat43) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat42) * u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;

    u_xlat16_31.x = u_xlat16_31.x + u_xlat16_31.x;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * (-u_xlat16_31.xxx) + (-u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_31.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_31.x = u_xlat16_31.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_31.x = u_xlat16_31.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_1 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_12.xyz, u_xlat16_31.x);

    u_xlat16_31.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_31.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_31.x = max(u_xlat16_31.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_31.x = log2(u_xlat16_31.x);
    u_xlat16_31.x = u_xlat16_31.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_31.x = exp2(u_xlat16_31.x);
    u_xlat16_31.x = u_xlat16_31.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat16_31.xxx;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 * u_xlat16_44 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_44 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_44;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_44);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_46) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(u_xlat42) + u_xlat11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_46 + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_44 = min(max(u_xlat16_44, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_44 = clamp(u_xlat16_44, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_44) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat9.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_44 = (-u_xlat16_17.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat1.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_44 * u_xlat16_3.x + u_xlat15;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 / u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 * u_xlat16_3.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_3.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 * u_xlat16_3.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_44 = min(max(u_xlat16_44, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_44 = clamp(u_xlat16_44, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_44 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 * u_xlat16_44;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_46 * u_xlat16_3.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_5.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_44) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = max(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = min(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_44 = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlatu0 = uint(int(u_xlat16_44));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz * vec3(u_xlat42) + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    for(uint u_xlatu_loop_1 = uint(0u) ; u_xlatu_loop_1<u_xlatu0 ; u_xlatu_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat28 = float(int(u_xlatu_loop_1));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb42 = !!(u_xlat28<2.0);
#else
        u_xlatb42 = u_xlat28<2.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_6.xy = (bool(u_xlatb42)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat1.x = u_xlat28 + -2.0;
        u_xlat28 = (u_xlatb42) ? u_xlat28 : u_xlat1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb28 = !!(u_xlat28<1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb28 = u_xlat28<1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_44 = (u_xlatb28) ? u_xlat16_6.x : u_xlat16_6.y;
        u_xlati28 = int(u_xlat16_44);
        u_xlat1.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPosition[u_xlati28].xyz;
        u_xlat42 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat42 = max(u_xlat42, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat43 = inversesqrt(u_xlat42);
        u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat43) * u_xlat1.xyz;
        u_xlat43 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat42);
        u_xlat42 = u_xlat42 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati28].x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati28].y;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat42 = min(max(u_xlat42, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat42 = clamp(u_xlat42, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat42 = u_xlat42 * u_xlat43;
        u_xlat16_44 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDir[u_xlati28].xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati28].z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati28].w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_44 = min(max(u_xlat16_44, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_44 = clamp(u_xlat16_44, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 * u_xlat16_44;
        u_xlat42 = u_xlat42 * u_xlat16_44;
        u_xlat16_44 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_44 = min(max(u_xlat16_44, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_44 = clamp(u_xlat16_44, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_44) * _AdditionalLightsColor[u_xlati28].xyz;
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat42) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
        u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}
SubProgram "gles " {
Keywords { "_ADDITIONAL_LIGHTS" "_MAIN_LIGHT_SHADOWS" "_SHTYPE_LERP" }
Local Keywords { "_BUMP_ON" "_COLOR_MASK" "_DEBUG_OFF" "_IFRAMP_ON" "_Mask_ON" }
"// hash: 11497d620b15399d
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[20];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat10_1.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat10_1.xyz = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlatb46 = _BlendMode==0.0;
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb46) ? 1.0 : u_xlat10_1.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat10_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat10_45 = texture2D(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_4 = vec4(u_xlat10_45) + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_4 = u_xlat16_4 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_4 = -abs(u_xlat16_4) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
    u_xlat16_4 = clamp(u_xlat16_4, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_4.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_50 = dot(u_xlat16_4, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 + u_xlat16_50;
    u_xlat16_47 = clamp(u_xlat16_47, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_4, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x + u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat10_1.zzz * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss));
    u_xlat16_3.x = max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(u_xlat16_3.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-u_xlat16_5.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_47) + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_7.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_7.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat45 = dot(u_xlat16_7.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
    u_xlat45 = max(u_xlat45, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat45 = inversesqrt(u_xlat45);
    u_xlat1.xzw = vec3(u_xlat45) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_2.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_49 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_49 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat8.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat45 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, vs_TEXCOORD7.xy).x;
    u_xlatb45 = u_xlat45<vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
    u_xlat16_49 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_50 = (u_xlatb45) ? 0.0 : _MainLightShadowParams.x;
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_49 + u_xlat16_50;
    u_xlatb45 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
    u_xlatb53 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
    u_xlatb45 = u_xlatb45 || u_xlatb53;
    u_xlat16_49 = (u_xlatb45) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_49;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * u_xlat16_18.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_47) * u_xlat9.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat45 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat45 = clamp(u_xlat45, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_18.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat1.xzw);
    u_xlat16_18.x = abs(u_xlat16_18.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_18.x = min(u_xlat16_18.x, 1.0);

    u_xlat54 = u_xlat16_2.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat53 * 0.125 + u_xlat54;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat10.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat53 = u_xlat53 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat54);
    u_xlat10.y = u_xlat53 + 0.125;

    u_xlat16_33.xy = u_xlat16_33.xy * vec2(_SHScale);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_33.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_33.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_33.x = u_xlat16_49 * u_xlat45;
    u_xlat16_33.x = u_xlat16_33.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_50 = (-u_xlat16_18.x) * u_xlat16_18.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_51 = u_xlat16_47 * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat53 = u_xlat16_51 * u_xlat16_51 + u_xlat16_50;
    u_xlat53 = u_xlat16_47 / u_xlat53;
    u_xlat53 = u_xlat53 * u_xlat53;
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_3.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat53 = u_xlat53 * u_xlat16_50;
    u_xlat53 = min(u_xlat53, 100.0);
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat53) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat45) * u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_50 = dot((-u_xlat1.xzw), u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 + u_xlat16_50;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_50)) + (-u_xlat1.xzw);
    u_xlat16_50 = (-u_xlat16_3.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_50;
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_12 = textureCube(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_12.xyz, u_xlat16_50);
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat10_12.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_50 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_50 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_50 = max(u_xlat16_50, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_50 = log2(u_xlat16_50);
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_50 = exp2(u_xlat16_50);
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat10_12.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_50);
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 * u_xlat16_47 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_47 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_47;
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat16_13.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_47);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_49) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(u_xlat45) + u_xlat11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_49 + _SHshadow;
    u_xlat16_47 = clamp(u_xlat16_47, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_47) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat1.xzw * u_xlat9.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_47 = (-u_xlat16_18.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat31 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat1.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_47 * u_xlat16_3.x + u_xlat31;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 / u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_18.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 * u_xlat16_3.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_3.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_47 = clamp(u_xlat16_47, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_47 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 * u_xlat16_47;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_49 * u_xlat16_3.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_5.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_47) * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = max(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = min(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat10_0.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = min(u_xlat16_48, 0.959999979);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * _RampTex_ST.x + _RampTex_ST.z;
    u_xlat0.y = 0.0;
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_RampTex, u_xlat0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_33.xxx * u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * _RampTexColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat10_1.yyy + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_47 = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlati0 = int(u_xlat16_47);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz * vec3(u_xlat45) + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    for(int u_xlati_loop_1 = 0 ; u_xlati_loop_1<u_xlati0 ; u_xlati_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat30 = float(u_xlati_loop_1);
        u_xlatb45 = u_xlat30<2.0;
        u_xlat16_6.xy = (bool(u_xlatb45)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat1.x = u_xlat30 + -2.0;
        u_xlat30 = (u_xlatb45) ? u_xlat30 : u_xlat1.x;
        u_xlatb30 = u_xlat30<1.0;
        u_xlat16_47 = (u_xlatb30) ? u_xlat16_6.x : u_xlat16_6.y;
        u_xlati30 = int(u_xlat16_47);
        u_xlat1.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPositionDynamicIndex(u_xlati30).xyz;
        u_xlat45 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat45 = max(u_xlat45, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat46 = inversesqrt(u_xlat45);
        u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat46) * u_xlat1.xyz;
        u_xlat46 = float(1.0) / u_xlat45;
        u_xlat45 = u_xlat45 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati30).x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati30).y;
        u_xlat45 = clamp(u_xlat45, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat45 = u_xlat45 * u_xlat46;
        u_xlat16_47 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDirDynamicIndex(u_xlati30).xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati30).z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati30).w;
        u_xlat16_47 = clamp(u_xlat16_47, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 * u_xlat16_47;
        u_xlat45 = u_xlat45 * u_xlat16_47;
        u_xlat16_47 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_47 = clamp(u_xlat16_47, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_47) * _AdditionalLightsColorDynamicIndex(u_xlati30).xyz;
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat45) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
        u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;

out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;

vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;

vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;

mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;

mediump vec3 u_xlat16_18;
float u_xlat30;
int u_xlati30;
bool u_xlatb30;
float u_xlat31;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_33;
float u_xlat45;
mediump float u_xlat16_45;
bool u_xlatb45;
float u_xlat46;
bool u_xlatb46;
mediump float u_xlat16_47;
mediump float u_xlat16_48;
mediump float u_xlat16_49;
mediump float u_xlat16_50;
mediump float u_xlat16_51;
float u_xlat53;
bool u_xlatb53;
float u_xlat54;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_1.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb46 = !!(_BlendMode==0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb46 = _BlendMode==0.0;
#endif
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb46) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_45 = texture(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_4 = vec4(u_xlat16_45) + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_4 = u_xlat16_4 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_4 = -abs(u_xlat16_4) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4 = min(max(u_xlat16_4, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4 = clamp(u_xlat16_4, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_4.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_50 = dot(u_xlat16_4, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 + u_xlat16_50;

    u_xlat16_7.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_7.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat45 = dot(u_xlat16_7.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
    u_xlat45 = max(u_xlat45, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat45 = inversesqrt(u_xlat45);

    u_xlat53 = u_xlat53 * u_xlat53;

#else
        u_xlatb30 = u_xlat30<1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_47 = (u_xlatb30) ? u_xlat16_6.x : u_xlat16_6.y;

#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];

uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;

vec4 u_xlat0;

vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

    u_xlat16_19.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_19.xyz;
    u_xlat16_19.xyz = u_xlat16_4.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_19.xyz;

    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xyw + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat10_0.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_MatTex, u_xlat10.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_35.xxx * u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * _MatTexColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat10_1.yyy + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_50 = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlati0 = int(u_xlat16_50);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz * vec3(u_xlat48) + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    for(int u_xlati_loop_1 = 0 ; u_xlati_loop_1<u_xlati0 ; u_xlati_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat32 = float(u_xlati_loop_1);
        u_xlatb48 = u_xlat32<2.0;
        u_xlat16_6.xy = (bool(u_xlatb48)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat1.x = u_xlat32 + -2.0;
        u_xlat32 = (u_xlatb48) ? u_xlat32 : u_xlat1.x;
        u_xlatb32 = u_xlat32<1.0;
        u_xlat16_50 = (u_xlatb32) ? u_xlat16_6.x : u_xlat16_6.y;
        u_xlati32 = int(u_xlat16_50);
        u_xlat1.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPositionDynamicIndex(u_xlati32).xyz;
        u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat48 = max(u_xlat48, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat49 = inversesqrt(u_xlat48);
        u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat49) * u_xlat1.xyz;
        u_xlat49 = float(1.0) / u_xlat48;
        u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati32).x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati32).y;
        u_xlat48 = clamp(u_xlat48, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat49;
        u_xlat16_50 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDirDynamicIndex(u_xlati32).xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati32).z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati32).w;
        u_xlat16_50 = clamp(u_xlat16_50, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 * u_xlat16_50;
        u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat16_50;
        u_xlat16_50 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_50 = clamp(u_xlat16_50, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_50) * _AdditionalLightsColorDynamicIndex(u_xlati32).xyz;
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat48) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
        u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _MatTex;

UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _ColorTex;
in mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
vec3 u_xlat11;
vec3 u_xlat12;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
uint u_xlatu16;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_19;
float u_xlat32;
int u_xlati32;
bool u_xlatb32;
float u_xlat33;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_35;
float u_xlat48;
mediump float u_xlat16_48;
bool u_xlatb48;
float u_xlat49;
bool u_xlatb49;
mediump float u_xlat16_50;
mediump float u_xlat16_51;
mediump float u_xlat16_52;
mediump float u_xlat16_53;
float u_xlat56;
bool u_xlatb56;
float u_xlat57;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(_NormalScale);
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_1.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb49 = !!(_BlendMode==0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb49 = _BlendMode==0.0;
#endif
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb49) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_48 = texture(_ColorTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_4 = vec4(u_xlat16_48) + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_4 = u_xlat16_4 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_4 = -abs(u_xlat16_4) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4 = min(max(u_xlat16_4, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4 = clamp(u_xlat16_4, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_19.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_19.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_19.xyz;
    u_xlat16_19.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_19.xyz;
    u_xlat16_19.xyz = u_xlat16_4.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_19.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_19.xyz;
    u_xlat16_53 = dot(u_xlat16_4, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 + u_xlat16_53;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_50 = min(max(u_xlat16_50, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_50 = clamp(u_xlat16_50, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_4, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x + u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss));
    u_xlat16_3.x = max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(u_xlat16_3.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-u_xlat16_5.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_50) + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_7.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;

#else

#endif

#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;

attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;

float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);

        u_xlat8.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPositionDynamicIndex(u_xlati32).xyz;
        u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
        u_xlat48 = max(u_xlat48, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat56 = inversesqrt(u_xlat48);
        u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat56) * u_xlat8.xyz;
        u_xlat56 = float(1.0) / u_xlat48;
        u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati32).x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati32).y;
        u_xlat48 = clamp(u_xlat48, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat56;
        u_xlat16_50 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDirDynamicIndex(u_xlati32).xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
        u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati32).z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati32).w;
        u_xlat16_50 = clamp(u_xlat16_50, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 * u_xlat16_50;
        u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat16_50;
        u_xlat16_50 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
        u_xlat16_50 = clamp(u_xlat16_50, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_50) * _AdditionalLightsColorDynamicIndex(u_xlati32).xyz;
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat48) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
        u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}
